title: Hana to Arisu satsujin jiken (2015)
genre: 动画 喜剧 犯罪
cast: Yû Aoi , Anne Suzuki , Shôko Aida , Sei Hiraizumi , Tomohiro Kaku , Ryô Katsuji , Midoriko Kimura , Tae Kimura , Haru Kuroki , Ranran Suzuki
summary: After her parents separate, 14 year-old Tetsuko (who will soon be nick-named Alice) moves with her mother to a new town in what she calls "The Boonies" and must enroll as a transfer student in a new middle school. She immediately finds herself bullied due being assigned the seat of "Judas" who is said to have been murdered over a year before. She is told that if anybody knows his fate it would be Hana, the recluse in the house next door, who has been unable to bring herself to attend class since "Judas" disappeared.　　  父母分居后，14岁的Tetsuko（她很快就会被昵称为Alice）和母亲搬到了她称之为“Boonies”的一个新城镇，必须在一所新的中学注册成为转学生。她立即发现自己受到了欺负，因为她被分配到了据说一年多前被谋杀的“犹大”的席位。她被告知，如果有人知道他的命运，那一定是隔壁房子里的隐士哈娜，自从“犹大”失踪后，她一直无法带自己去上课。

title: Xiong chu mo
genre: 动画
cast: Siobhan Lumsden , Joseph S. Lambert , Gene Hobbs III , Paul 'Maxx' Rinehart , Ethan Kiely , Jenny Ansell , Che Devereux Scott Rinehart , Wan Danqing , Chen Guang , Ma Haolun , Yutian Meng , Xiaodong Sun , Xiao Tan , Veronica J. Valentini , Zhang Wei , Xin Yuan , Bingjun Zhang
summary: A story of friends old and new, of being lost but most importantly being found; The Big Top Secret follows Briar as he is whisked away from the home he knows and plunged head first into the ranks of a traveling circus. The struggling circus, led by Hugo the Gorilla, is on its last leg and in desperate need of a boost. Frustrated with his brother, Bramble, and the rest of his forest friends, Briar finds a new and welcoming home among Wolfgang's Big Top. Briar brings life back to the circus and quickly finds happiness in his new life filled with new friends and fame. While rising to the top has its benefits, it also comes with a price. After searching high and low, Bramble and his forest friends are thrilled to have found their lost Briar, but Briar is not so sure that he wants to be found. He doesn't want to leave his perfect new life at the big top but even the most perfect-seeming things have dark sides. Through trials and chases and trains, all of the animals learn what it is to belong and the true meaning of family.　　  一个关于新老朋友的故事，一个关于失去但最重要的是被找到的故事；《最高机密》（The Big Top Secret）讲述了布莱尔（Briar）被带离他认识的家，一头扎进一个巡回马戏团的行列。由大猩猩雨果领导的马戏团正处于挣扎中，目前已奄奄一息，亟需提振。布莱尔对他的兄弟布兰布尔和其他森林朋友感到失望，他在沃尔夫冈的大山顶找到了一个新的、受欢迎的家。布莱尔将生活带回马戏团，并很快在充满新朋友和名气的新生活中找到幸福。虽然上升到顶峰有其好处，但也有其代价。在到处寻找之后，布兰布尔和他的森林朋友们都很激动地发现了他们丢失的布莱尔，但布莱尔并不确定自己是否想被找到。他不想把自己完美的新生活留在高层，但即使是最完美的东西也有阴暗的一面。通过试验、追逐和训练，所有的动物都学会了归属和家庭的真正意义。

summary: Briar and Bramble, the two bear brothers always getting in Vick's way, are in for a rude awakening. Vick heads out to shrink them out of his life. In the tussle the device is tossed and all three of them are caught in the beam and find themselves looking up at the rest of the world. The tiny team have to get back to the device to reverse the effects but their efforts are intercepted by Vick's dad. He comes back to apologize to Vick but leaves with the machine when he can't find him. summary: Genetics have never been so hilarious. A thrilling new place opens on Pine Tree Mountain, "Wild Land", that offers a legendary experience. By wearing a gene-altering bracelet, guests can transform themselves into a variety of animals. Vick discovers that Wild life is hosting a competition with a massive grand prize and decides to enter. He teams up with Bramble and a mysterious man named Leon, astonishingly winning the tournament. Soon afterwards, Leon is caught trying to secretly copy the park data by the owner, Tom, and Vick discovers that hybrid guests are going feral and attacking others - Who is the mysterious Leon? Is Tom the mastermind Vick has to fight.　　  遗传学从来没有这么搞笑过。松树山“荒原”上开辟了一个激动人心的新地方，提供了一种传奇的体验。通过佩戴基因改变手镯，客人可以把自己变成各种各样的动物。维克发现《野生动物》正在举办一场比赛，并获得了巨额大奖，于是决定参赛。他与布兰布尔（Bramble）和一位名叫莱昂（Leon）的神秘男子搭档，令人惊讶地赢得了比赛。不久之后，里昂被主人汤姆抓到试图秘密复制公园数据，维克发现混血游客变得凶猛并攻击他人——神秘的里昂是谁？汤姆是维克必须战斗的策划者吗。

title: Histoire immortelle (TV Movie 1968)
genre: 剧情
cast: Orson Welles , Jeanne Moreau , Roger Coggio , Norman Eshley , Fernando Rey
summary: The Portuguese colony of Macao in the 19th century. Mr. Clay is a very rich merchant and the subject of town gossip. He has spent many years in China and is now quite old. He likes his clerk Levinsky to read the company's accounts to him at night for relaxation. Tonight Mr. Clay recounts a true story he heard years before about a rich man who paid a poor sailor 5 guineas to father a child with his beautiful young wife. Levinsky says that's a popular old sailor's legend and not true. Mr. Clay has no heir for his fortune and no wife either. He resolves to make the story true... Levinsky approaches Virginie, another clerk's mistress, and strikes a bargain for 300 guineas. Now to find the sailor...　　  19世纪葡萄牙殖民地澳门。克莱先生是一位非常富有的商人，也是镇上流言蜚语的话题。他在中国呆了很多年，现在已经很老了。他喜欢他的职员列文斯基晚上读公司的账目给他放松。今晚，克莱先生讲述了他多年前听过的一个真实故事，讲述了一个富人付给一个可怜的水手5几内亚，让他和他年轻漂亮的妻子生下一个孩子。莱文斯基说，这是一个受欢迎的老水手的传说，但不是真的。克莱先生没有财产继承人，也没有妻子。他决心使这个故事成为事实。。。莱文斯基走近另一位店员的情妇维吉尼（Virginie），讨价还价300几尼。现在去找水手。。。

title: The Incident (1967)
genre: 犯罪 剧情 惊悚
cast: Tony Musante , Martin Sheen , Beau Bridges , Brock Peters , Ruby Dee , Jack Gilford , Thelma Ritter , Ed McMahon , Diana Van der Vlis , Mike Kellin , Jan Sterling , Gary Merrill , Robert Fields , Robert Bannard , Victor Arnold , Donna Mills , Kathleen Smith , Henry Proach
summary: Stark melodrama about two thrill-seeking tough guys who terrorize late-night passengers on a New York City train. The random victims are more concerned with their own problems than with helping each other; they pray that they won't be next. But it will take much more than prayer to end this nightmare of fear and violence. Both Martin Sheen and Tony Musante make their film debuts as the hoodlums.　　  斯塔克（Stark）讲述了两个寻求刺激的硬汉恐吓纽约火车上深夜乘客的情节剧。随机受害者更关心自己的问题，而不是相互帮助；他们祈祷自己不会成为下一个。但要结束这场恐惧和暴力的噩梦，需要的不仅仅是祈祷。马丁·辛（Martin Sheen）和托尼·穆桑特（Tony Musante）都以流氓身份首次亮相。

title: The Incredible Shrinking Man (1957)
genre: 恐怖 科幻
cast: Grant Williams , Randy Stuart , April Kent , Paul Langton , Raymond Bailey , William Schallert , Frank J. Scannell , Helene Marshall , Diana Darrin , Billy Curtis , Chet Brandenburg , John Hiestand , Joe LaBarba , Perk Lazelle , Lock Martin , Orangey , Regis Parton , Charles Perry
summary: Scott Carey and his wife Louise are sunning themselves on their cabin cruiser, the small craft adrift on a calm sea. While his wife is below deck, a low mist passes over him. Scott, lying in the sun, is sprinkled with glittery particles that quickly evaporate. Later he is accidentally sprayed with an insecticide while driving and, in the next few days, he finds that he has begun to shrink. First just a few inches, so that his clothes no longer fit, then a little more. Soon he is only three feet tall, and a national curiosity. At six inches tall he can only live in a doll's house and even that becomes impossible when his cat breaks in. Scott flees to the cellar, his wife thinks he has been eaten by the cat and the door to the cellar is closed, trapping him in the littered room where, menaced by a giant spider, he struggles to survive.　　  斯科特·凯里（Scott Carey）和他的妻子路易斯（Louise）正在他们的巡洋舰上晒太阳，这艘小船在平静的海面上漂流。当他的妻子在甲板下时，薄雾从他身上掠过。斯科特躺在阳光下，身上撒着闪闪发光的微粒，这些微粒很快就会蒸发掉。后来，他在开车时不小心喷了杀虫剂，在接下来的几天里，他发现自己开始萎缩。首先只有几英寸，这样他的衣服就不合身了，然后再多一点。很快，他就只有三英尺高，成为了全国的好奇心。六英寸高的斯科特只能住在洋娃娃的房子里，而当他的猫闯入时，这就变得不可能了。斯科特逃到地窖，他的妻子认为他被猫吃掉了，地窖的门也关上了，他被困在一个乱七八糟的房间里，在那里，他受到一只巨大蜘蛛的威胁，挣扎着求生。

title: The Innocents (1961)
genre: 剧情 恐怖 悬疑
cast: Deborah Kerr , Peter Wyngarde , Megs Jenkins , Michael Redgrave , Martin Stephens , Pamela Franklin , Clytie Jessop , Isla Cameron , Eric Woodburn
summary: In Victorian England, the uncle (Sir Michael Redgrave) of orphaned niece Flora (Pamela Franklin) and nephew Miles (Martin Stephens) hires Miss Giddens (Deborah Kerr) as governess to raise the children at his estate with total independence and authority. Soon after her arrival, Miss Giddens comes to believe that the spirits of the former governess Miss Jessel (Clytie Jessop) and valet Peter Quint (Peter Wyngarde) are possessing the children. Miss Giddens decides to help the children to face and exorcise the spirits.　　  在维多利亚时代的英国，孤儿侄女弗洛拉（帕梅拉·富兰克林饰）的叔叔（迈克尔·雷德格雷夫爵士）和侄子迈尔斯（马丁·斯蒂芬斯饰）聘请吉登斯小姐（黛博拉·科尔饰）担任家庭教师，以完全独立和权威的方式抚养其庄园中的孩子。到达后不久，吉登斯小姐开始相信前家庭教师杰塞尔小姐（Clytie Jessop）和贴身男仆彼得·昆特（Peter Wyngarde）的灵魂控制着孩子们。吉登斯小姐决定帮助孩子们面对和驱除鬼魂。

title: The Intern (2015)
genre: 喜剧 剧情
cast: Robert De Niro , Anne Hathaway , Rene Russo , Anders Holm , JoJo Kushner , Andrew Rannells , Adam Devine , Zack Pearlman , Jason Orley , Christina Scherer , Nat Wolff , Linda Lavin , Celia Weston , Steve Vinovich , C.J. Wilson , Mary Kay Place , Erin Mackey , Christina Brucato
summary: A retired 70-year-old widower, Ben (played by Robert De Niro), is bored with retired life. He applies to a be a senior intern at an online fashion retailer and gets the position. The founder of the company is Jules Ostin (Anne Hathaway), a tireless, driven, demanding, dynamic workaholic. title: Contratiempo (2016)
genre: 犯罪 剧情 悬疑
cast: Mario Casas , Ana Wagener , Jose Coronado , Bárbara Lennie , Francesc Orella , Paco Tous , David Selvas , Iñigo Gastesi , San Yélamos , Manel Dueso , Blanca Martínez , Pere Brasó , Jordi Brunet , Bobby Gonzalez , Martina Hurtado , Ruth Llopis , Jordi Llordella , Annick Weerts
summary: Adrián Doria, a wealthy businessman named Man of the Year due to his high-tech company and his trade agreements with the Asian market, meets Virginia Goodman, a veteran lawyer expert in witness preparation and judicial declaration, recommended by Adrián's lawyer Felix Leiva in order to create a credible defense. Arrested by the police in a mountain hotel room with the corpse of his lover at his side, photographer Laura Vidal, Adrián talks Virginia about the crime and his relationship with Laura, revealing that both suffered a car crash where a man called Daniel Garrido died, and how Laura manipulated Adrián to avoid the jail by Daniel's death. At the same time that Félix is looking for a clue that it could change the course of the events, Virginia and Adrián keep talking about the case but her, unconvinced of the Adrián's testimony, forces him to clear the dark points of his history, in a puzzle where the truth and the lie are easily exchangeable.　　  阿德里安·多里亚（Adrián Doria）是一位富有的商人，因其高科技公司和与亚洲市场的贸易协议而被命名为年度风云人物，他会见了维吉尼亚·古德曼（Virginia Goodman），这位资深的律师是证人准备和司法声明方面的专家，由阿德里安的律师费利克斯·莱瓦（Felix Leiva）推荐，以建立一个可信的辩护。摄影师劳拉·维达尔（Laura Vidal）在山间酒店房间被警方逮捕，身边还有情人的尸体。阿德里安（Adrián）向弗吉尼亚讲述了这起犯罪以及他与劳拉的关系，透露两人都遭遇了一起车祸，一名名叫丹尼尔·加里多（Daniel Garrido）的男子死亡，以及劳拉是如何操纵阿德里安以避免因丹尼尔的死亡而入狱的。与此同时，费利克斯正在寻找可能改变事件进程的线索，维吉尼亚和阿德里安一直在谈论这个案件，但她不相信阿德里安的证词，迫使他清除历史的黑暗点，在这个谜团中，真相和谎言很容易互换。

title: The Hurricane Heist (2018)
genre: 动作 冒险 犯罪
cast: Toby Kebbell , Maggie Grace , Ryan Kwanten , Ralph Ineson , Melissa Bolona , Ben Cross , Jamie Andrew Cutler , Christian Contreras , Jimmy Walker , Ed Birch , Moyo Akandé , James Barriscale , Erik Rondell , Mark Basnight , Keith D. Evans , Mark Rhino Smith , Brooke Johnston , Patrick McAuley
summary: In 1992 Alabama, Will and Breeze Rutledge are evacuating from the destructive Category 5 Hurricane Andrew with their dad. However, their truck gets stuck after avoiding a toppling tree in front of them and they are forced to take refuge in a nearby house. While trying to save the truck from blowing away, strong winds blow a water tank loose and it crushes their dad, killing him. In present day, another destructive hurricane named Tammy approaches the town in Alabama. Treasury agent Casey Corbyn is ordered by fellow employee Randy Moreno to summon Breeze, who now works as a handyman, and whose brother Will is a meteorologist, to fix the generator at a cash storage facility. While she is out of the facility, rogue Treasury agents, led by Connor Perkins, infiltrate the facility and hold employee Moreno hostage..　　  1992年，阿拉巴马州，威尔和布雷斯·拉特利奇正与他们的父亲一起从破坏性的5级飓风安德鲁中撤离。然而，他们的卡车在躲避面前一棵倒下的树后被卡住了，他们被迫在附近的房子里避难。当试图拯救卡车免受风吹走时，强风将一个水箱吹松，将他们的父亲压死。今天，另一场名为塔米的破坏性飓风逼近阿拉巴马州的小镇。财政部特工凯西·科尔宾（Casey Corbyn）接到同事兰迪·莫雷诺（Randy Moreno）的命令，要求他召集布雷兹（Breeze）来修理一个现金储存设施的发电机。布雷兹现在是一名杂工，他的兄弟威尔（Will）是一名气象学家。当她离开工厂时，由康诺·帕金斯（Connor Perkins）领导的流氓财政部特工潜入工厂并将员工莫雷诺（Moreno）扣为人质。。

title: The House That Jack Built (2018)
genre: 犯罪 剧情 恐怖
cast: Matt Dillon , Bruno Ganz , Uma Thurman , Siobhan Fallon Hogan , Sofie Gråbøl , Riley Keough , Jeremy Davies , Jack McKenzie , Mathias Hjelm , Ed Speleers , Emil Tholstrup , Marijana Jankovic , Carina Skenhede , Rocco Day , Cohen Day , Robert Jezek , Osy Ikhile , Christian Arnold
summary: USA in the 1970s. We follow the highly intelligent Jack over a span of 12 years and are introduced to the murders that define Jack's development as a serial killer. We experience the story from Jack's point of view, while he postulates that each murder is an artwork in itself. As the inevitable police intervention is drawing nearer, he is taking greater and greater risks in his attempt to create the ultimate artwork. Along the way we experience Jack's descriptions of his personal condition, problems and thoughts through a recurring conversation with the unknown Verge--a grotesque mixture of sophistry mixed with an almost childlike self-pity and psychopathic explanations. The House That Jack Built is a dark and sinister story, yet presented through a philosophical and occasional humorous tale.　　  20世纪70年代的美国。我们在12年的时间里一直关注着这位聪明绝顶的杰克，并向他介绍了那些将杰克发展成为连环杀手的谋杀案。我们从杰克的角度来体验这个故事，而他假设每一件谋杀案本身就是一件艺术品。随着不可避免的警察干预越来越近，他在尝试创作终极艺术品时冒着越来越大的风险。在这一过程中，我们通过与未知的Verge的反复对话，体验了Jack对他的个人状况、问题和思想的描述，这是一种诡辩与近乎孩子气的自怜和心理变态的解释交织在一起的怪诞混合物。杰克建造的房子是一个黑暗而险恶的故事，但通过一个哲学和偶尔的幽默故事呈现出来。

title: Ningen no jôken (1959)
genre: 剧情 历史 战争
cast: Tatsuya Nakadai , Michiyo Aratama , Chikage Awashima , Ineko Arima , Keiji Sada , Sô Yamamura , Akira Ishihama , Kôji Nanbara , Seiji Miyaguchi , Tôru Abe , Masao Mishima , Eitarô Ozawa , Kôji Mitsui , Akitake Kôno , Nobuo Nakamura , Kyû Sazanka , Eijirô Tôno , Yasushi Nagata
summary: In World War II, the pacifist and humanist Japanese Kaji accepts to travel with his wife Michiko to the tiny Manchurian village Loh Hu Liong to work as supervisor in an iron ore mine to avoid to be summoned to the military service. Kaji works with Okishima (Sô Yamamura) and he implements a better treatment to the laborers and improves the mine production. When the feared Kempetai (The "Military Police Corps", the military police arm of the Imperial Japanese Army from 1881 to 1945) brings six hundred Chinese POWs to the mine, Kaji negotiates with their leaders expecting them to control their comrades. However the methods of Kaji upset the corrupt system in the site, and the foreman Furuya (Kôji Mitsui) plots a scheme to use the naive Chen (Akira Ishihama) to turn off the electrical power of the barbwire fences to allow the prisoners to escape. When seven prisoners are falsely accused of an attempt of fleeing, a cruel Kempetai sergeant uses his sword to behead the prisoners. When Kaji protests, the POWs react sparing the lives of four prisoners but Kaji is arrested and tortured. When he is released, he is summoned to join the army and accused of being Red.　　  在第二次世界大战中，日本和平主义者和人道主义者卡吉（Kaji）同意与妻子美智子（Michiko）一起前往满洲的一个小村庄Loh Hu Liong，在一个铁矿石矿担任监督员，以避免被征召服兵役。Kaji与Okishima（山村）合作，他对工人实行更好的待遇，并提高了矿山产量。当令人恐惧的坚佩台（“宪兵队”，1881年至1945年日本帝国军的宪兵部队）将600名中国战俘带到矿井时，卡吉与他们的领导人谈判，希望他们能控制自己的战友。然而，卡吉的方法扰乱了现场的腐败体系，工头福鲁雅（三井县）策划了一个计划，利用天真的陈水扁（石仓明彦饰）关闭铁丝网的电源，让囚犯逃跑。当七名囚犯被诬告企图逃跑时，一名残忍的肯佩泰中士用剑将囚犯斩首。当卡吉抗议时，战俘们的反应是保全了四名囚犯的生命，但卡吉被逮捕并遭到酷刑。当他被释放后，他被召入伍，并被指控为红色。

title: Ningen no jôken (1959)
genre: 剧情 历史 战争
cast: Tatsuya Nakadai , Michiyo Aratama , Kokinji Katsura , Jun Tatara , Michirô Minami , Kei Satô , Kunie Tanaka , Ryôhei Uchida , Kan Yanagiya , Kenjirô Uemura , Kaneko Iwasaki , Mayumi Kurata , Taketoshi Naitô , Hideo Kidokoro , Yoshiaki Aoki , Rô Ose , Tamotsu Tamura , Ryoji Ito
summary: Kaji is sent to the Japanese army labeled Red and is mistreated by the vets. Along his assignment, Kaji witnesses cruelties in the army; he revolts against the abusive treatment spent to the recruit Obara that commits suicide; he also sees his friend Shinjô Ittôhei defecting to the Russian border; and he ends in the front to fight a lost battle against the Russian tanks division.　　  卡吉被送往日本军队，并被贴上红色标签，遭到兽医的虐待。在执行任务的过程中，卡吉目睹了军队中的残酷行为；他反对对自杀的新兵奥巴拉进行虐待；他还看到他的朋友辛吉·伊托赫伊叛逃到俄罗斯边境；最后，他在前线与俄罗斯坦克师进行了一场失败的战斗。

title: The Silence of the Lambs (1991)
genre: 犯罪 剧情 恐怖
cast: Jodie Foster  ,  Anthony Hopkins  ,  Scott Glenn  ,  Ted Levine  ,  Anthony Heald  ,  Brooke Smith  ,  Diane Baker  ,  Kasi Lemmons  ,  Charles Napier  ,  Tracey Walter  ,  Roger Corman  ,  Ron Vawter  ,  Danny Darst  ,  Jeffrie Lane  ,  Frankie Faison  ,  Paul Lazar  ,  Dan Butler  ,  Chris Isaak
summary: F.B.I. trainee Clarice Starling (Jodie Foster) works hard to advance her career, while trying to hide or put behind her West Virginia roots, of which if some knew, would automatically classify her as being backward or white trash. After graduation, she aspires to work in the agency's Behavioral Science Unit under the leadership of Jack Crawford (Scott Glenn). While she is still a trainee, Crawford asks her to question Dr. Hannibal Lecter (Sir Anthony Hopkins), a psychiatrist imprisoned, thus far, for eight years in maximum security isolation for being a serial killer who cannibalized his victims. Clarice is able to figure out the assignment is to pick Lecter's brains to help them solve another serial murder case, that of someone coined by the media as "Buffalo Bill" (Ted Levine), who has so far killed five victims, all located in the eastern U.S., all young women, who are slightly overweight (especially around the hips), all who were drowned in natural bodies of water, and all who were stripped of large swaths of skin. She also figures that Crawford chose her, as a woman, to be able to trigger some emotional response from Lecter. After speaking to Lecter for the first time, she realizes that everything with him will be a psychological game, with her often having to read between the very cryptic lines he provides. She has to decide how much she will play along, as his request in return for talking to him is to expose herself emotionally to him. The case takes a more dire turn when a sixth victim is discovered, this one from who they are able to retrieve a key piece of evidence, if Lecter is being forthright as to its meaning. A potential seventh victim is high profile Catherine Martin (Brooke Smith), the daughter of Senator Ruth Martin (Diane Baker), which places greater scrutiny on the case as they search for a hopefully still alive Catherine. Who may factor into what happens is Dr. Frederick Chilton (Anthony Heald), the warden at the prison, an opportunist who sees the higher profile with Catherine, meaning a higher profile for himself if he can insert himself successfully into the proceedings.　　  FBI实习生克拉丽斯·斯塔琳（朱迪·福斯特饰）努力工作，以推进自己的事业，同时试图隐藏或掩盖自己的西弗吉尼亚血统，如果有人知道，她会自动被归类为落后或白人垃圾。毕业后，她渴望在杰克·克劳福德（斯科特·格伦饰）领导下的机构行为科学部门工作。当她还是一名实习生时，克劳福德要求她询问汉尼拔·莱克特医生（安东尼·霍普金斯爵士）。汉尼拔是一名精神科医生，由于是一名连环杀手，残害了受害者，迄今为止，她被监禁了八年，受到了最大程度的安全隔离。克拉丽斯能够理解，任务是挑选莱克特的大脑，帮助他们解决另一起连环谋杀案，即媒体虚构的“水牛比尔”（特德·莱文），迄今为止，他已经杀害了五名受害者，所有受害者都位于美国东部，都是年轻女性，她们都稍微超重（尤其是臀部周围），所有被自然水体淹死的人，以及所有被剥去大片皮肤的人。她还认为，克劳福德选择她作为一名女性，是为了能够引发莱克特的一些情绪反应。在第一次与莱克特交谈后，她意识到与他在一起的一切都将是一场心理游戏，她经常不得不阅读他提供的非常隐晦的台词。她必须决定自己将在多大程度上配合，因为他要求与他交谈的回报是向他暴露自己的情感。当第六名受害者被发现时，案件发生了更可怕的转变，如果莱克特直言不讳地说出其含义的话，这个受害者就是他们能够从中检索到关键证据的人。潜在的第七个受害者是高调的凯瑟琳·马丁（布鲁克·史密斯饰），她是参议员露丝·马丁（戴安·贝克饰）的女儿，在他们寻找一个可能还活着的凯瑟琳时，她对案件进行了更严格的审查。可能会考虑到发生的事情的是监狱典狱长弗雷德里克·奇尔顿博士（安东尼·希尔德饰），他是一个机会主义者，他看到了凯瑟琳的更高姿态，这意味着如果他能成功地介入诉讼，他自己的姿态就会更高。

genre: 剧情 历史 战争

summary: Part three of a trilogy. After the Japanese defeat to the Russians in the last episode, Kaji, the Japanese soldier and humanistic protagonist, leads the last remaining men through Manchuria. Intent on returning to his dear wife and his old life, Kaji faces great odds in a variety of different harrowing circumstances as he and his fellow men sneak behind enemy lines. Ultimately, he finds himself in the exact opposite position he held in the first episode

title: The Hummingbird Project (2018)
genre: 剧情 惊悚
cast: Jesse Eisenberg , Alexander Skarsgård , Salma Hayek , Michael Mando , Johan Heldenbergh , Ayisha Issa , Mark Slacke , Sarah Goldberg , Frank Schorpion , Kwasi Songui , Conrad Pla , Julian Bailey , Jessica Greco , Robert Reynolds , Anna Maguire , Ryan Ali , Amanda Silveira , Kaniehtiio Horn
summary: In this modern epic, Kim Nguyen exposes the ruthless edge of our increasingly digital world. Cousins from New York, Vincent (Eisenberg) and Anton (Skarsgård) are players in the high-stakes game of High Frequency Trading, where winning is measured in milliseconds. Their dream? To build a fiber-optic cable straight between Kansas and New Jersey, making them millions. But nothing is straightforward for this flawed pair. Anton is the brains, Vincent is the hustler, and together they push each other and everyone around them to breaking point on their quixotic adventure. Constantly breathing down their necks is their old boss Eva Torres (Hayek) a powerful, intoxicating and manipulative trader who will stop at nothing to come between them and beat them at their own game. No matter what the cost, Vincent and Anton are determined to cut through America, only to find redemption at the end of their line, not through money, but through family and reconnecting to the land.　　  在这部现代史诗中，金阮揭露了我们日益数字化的世界的残酷边缘。来自纽约的堂兄弟、Vincent（Eisenberg）和Anton（Skarsgárd）是高频交易这一高风险游戏的玩家，其中的获胜以毫秒为单位。他们的梦想？在堪萨斯州和新泽西州之间建造一条直达的光纤电缆，使他们获得数百万美元的收入。但对于这对有缺陷的搭档来说，没有什么是直截了当的。安东是智者，文森特是骗子，他们一起推动对方和周围的每个人在他们的唐吉诃德冒险中达到临界点。他们的老老板伊娃·托雷斯（哈耶克饰）一直在紧盯着他们，他是一个强大、令人陶醉、善于操纵的交易员，他会不顾一切地阻挠他们，在自己的比赛中击败他们。无论付出多大代价，文森特和安东都决心穿越美国，只为在他们的终点找到救赎，而不是通过金钱，而是通过家庭和重新连接土地。

title: The Hustler (1961)
genre: 剧情 运动
cast: Paul Newman , Jackie Gleason , Piper Laurie , George C. Scott , Myron McCormick , Murray Hamilton , Michael Constantine , Stefan Gierasch , Clifford A. Pellow , Jake LaMotta , Gordon B. Clarke , Alexander Rose , Carolyn Coates , Carl York , Vincent Gardenia , William Adams , Tom Ahearne , Charles Andre
summary: "Fast" Eddie Felson is a small-time pool hustler with a lot of talent but a self-destructive attitude. His bravado causes him to challenge the legendary "Minnesota Fats" to a high-stakes match, but he loses in a heartbreaking marathon. Now broke and without his long-time manager, Felson faces an uphill battle to regain his confidence and his game. It isn't until he hits rock bottom that he agrees to join up with ruthless and cutthroat manager Bert Gordon. Gordon agrees to take him on the road to learn the ropes. But Felson soon realizes that making it to the top could cost him his soul, and perhaps his girlfriend. Will he decide that this is too steep a price to pay in time to save himself?　　  “Fast”艾迪·费尔森是一个时间不长的台球骗子，他有很多天赋，但却有自我建设的态度。他的虚张声势使他向传奇的“明尼苏达胖子队”发起了一场高风险比赛，但他在一场令人心碎的马拉松比赛中输了。现在他身无分文，没有了长期的教练，费尔森面临着一场艰难的战斗，以重新获得信心和比赛。直到他跌入谷底，他才同意与冷酷无情的经理伯特·戈登（Bert Gordon）合作。戈登同意带他上路学习诀窍。但费尔森很快意识到，要登上顶峰，可能会让他付出灵魂的代价，甚至可能会让他的女友付出代价。他会认为这是一个太高的代价，不能及时支付来拯救自己吗？

genre: 犯罪 剧情 爱情
cast: Don Johnson , Virginia Madsen , Jennifer Connelly , Charles Martin Smith , William Sadler , Jerry Hardin , Barry Corbin , Leon Rippy , Jack Nance , Virgil Frye , John Hawker , Margaret Bowman , Debra Cole , Karen Culley , Cody Haynes , George Haynes , James N. Harrell , Edith Mills
summary: When the drifter Harry Madox reaches a small town in Texas, he gets a job as used car salesman with the dealer George Harshaw and settles down in a hotel room. During a fire, Harry observes that the local bank is left empty and open without any security. Soon he plots a scheme to rob the bank, provoking a fire in his room to distract the employees. When Harry meets George's wife Dolly Harshaw, the easy woman teases him and they have sex. title: Dung fong sam hap (1993)
genre: 动作 奇幻 惊悚
cast: Michelle Yeoh , Anita Mui , Maggie Cheung , Damian Lau , Anthony Chau-Sang Wong , Paul Chun , James Pax , Shi-Kwan Yen , Guerin Barry , Cheuk Yan Chan , Mimi Chu , Keith Ferguson , Jessica Gee-George , Kam-Moon Ho , Philip Keung , Tom Konkle , Siu-Kay Lee , Wendee Lee
summary: The all-female Heroic Trio are Tung (Wonder Woman), Chat (Thief Catcher), a mercenary, and Ching (Invisible Woman). Initially, they're on opposing sides - the invisible Ching is kidnapping newborn male babies for her evil master, Tung is trying to solve the crime (rather more effectively than her policeman husband, who is unaware of her secret identity), and Chat, who was formerly employed by Ching's evil master, is trying to sell her services and inside knowledge to the police. But all three have something in common buried deep in their past...　　  全女性英雄三人组包括童（神奇女侠）、查（捉贼贼）、佣兵和清（隐形女侠）。起初，他们是对立的——隐形的秦正为她的邪恶主人绑架新生男婴，董正试图破案（比她的警察丈夫更有效，因为她不知道自己的秘密身份），而查特则是秦的邪恶主人的雇员，试图向警方出售她的服务和内幕消息。但这三个人在过去有着共同点。。。

title: The Hidden (1987)
genre: 恐怖 科幻 惊悚
cast: Kyle MacLachlan , Michael Nouri , Claudia Christian , Clarence Felder , Clu Gulager , Ed O'Ross , William Boyett , Richard Brooks , Larry Cedar , Katherine Cannon , John McCann , Chris Mulkey , Lin Shaye , James Luisi , Frank Renzulli , Duane Davis , Kristen Clayton , Whitney Reis
summary: An alien parasite with the ability to possess human bodies goes on a violent crime spree in LA, committing dozens of murders and robberies. In pursuit of the extraterrestrial criminal is an FBI agent, and the local officer investigating the rash of violence. As they close in on the vicious intruder, the city faces a brutal threat like no other it has ever encountered.　　  一种能够控制人体的外星寄生虫在洛杉矶肆虐，犯下数十起谋杀和抢劫罪。追捕外星人的罪犯是一名FBI特工，而当地官员正在调查这起暴力事件。当他们逼近凶恶的入侵者时，这座城市面临着前所未有的残酷威胁。

cast: Toshirô Mifune , Misa Uehara , Minoru Chiaki , Kamatari Fujiwara , Susumu Fujita , Takashi Shimura , Eiko Miyoshi , Toshiko Higuchi , Yû Fujiki , Yoshio Tsuchiya , Kokuten Kôdô , Takeshi Katô , Kôji Mitsui , Toranosuke Ogawa , Kichijirô Ueda , Nakajirô Tomita , Yoshifumi Tajima , Ikio Sawamura
summary: The story follows two greedy peasants in feudal Japan, Tahei and Matashichi, who are returning home from a failed attempt to profit from a war between neighboring clans. En Route they encounter the remnants of the defeated tribe that consists, most notably, of a famous General and a Princess who are hiding out in a fortress in the mountains. General Rokurota Makabe and Princess Yuki need to escape into allied territory with their large supply of gold so that they can rebuild their shattered clan. To do this the Peasants are tricked into helping them, with the promise that they will receive a large share of the gold when the destination is reached. Along the way, the General's prowess is put to the test as he must guide the 4, and later 5 with the inclusion of a freed slave, through close encounters with the pursuing enemy, and out of difficult situations the bumbling peasants manage to get them into.　　  故事讲述的是封建日本的两个贪婪的农民，大尾和松石，他们试图从相邻氏族之间的战争中获利，但失败了。途中，他们遇到了战败部落的残余，其中最著名的是一位著名将军和一位公主，他们躲在山里的一座堡垒里。Rokurota Makabe将军和Yuki公主需要带着大量黄金逃往盟国领土，以便重建他们支离破碎的氏族。为了做到这一点，农民们被骗去帮助他们，并承诺在到达目的地时，他们将获得大部分黄金。在这一过程中，将军的能力受到了考验，因为他必须带领4人，以及后来的5人，包括一名自由的奴隶，与追击的敌人进行近距离接触，走出困境，笨手笨脚的农民设法让他们进入。

title: Kakushi ken
genre: 剧情 历史 爱情
cast: Masatoshi Nagase , Takako Matsu , Hidetaka Yoshioka , Yukiyoshi Ozawa , Tomoko Tabata , Chieko Baishô , Kunie Tanaka , Toshiki Ayata , Hiroshi Kanbe , Sachiko Mitsumoto , Reiko Takashima , Satoko Yamamura , Nana Saito , Kazuhiko Kasai , Ryôta Satô , Jun Maeda , Takai Mizuno , Yoshiko Shinohara
summary: During the time of change of the mid-19th Century, Yaichiro is bid farewell by his fellow samurai friends Munezo and Samon as he leaves their clan's fiefdom on the northwest coast of Japan (Unasaka) to take an important position within the shogunate in far away Edo. Munezo has lived modestly with his mother and sister Shino after his father was forced into suicide after the failure of a bridge project. Kie, a farm girl serves them as a maid in their house. As time passes, Munezo's sister marries Samon, his mother dies, Kie is married into a merchant family, and he is required to learn western methods of warfare such as the use of artillery and firearms from an official sent from Edo. Learning that Kie is ill due to abuse, he rescues her from her husband's family. Although sharing mutual affection and respect, a marriage between Munezo and Kie is still impossible due to different castes, and when he, now a bachelor, is criticized for her serving in his house, Munezo sends her back to her father's farm. After being caught in a failed political intrigue, Yaichiro is sent home in disgrace and imprisoned in solitary confinement. After Yaichiro escapes, Munezo is ordered to prove his innocence from complicity by killing his old friend, and he seeks the help of his old teacher, the sword master Kansai Toda. Although Yaichiro had been the better swordsman when they studied together, Toda entrusted the secret of the "Hidden Blade" only to Munezo. Toda now teaches him a new technique to use as he prepares to face Yaichiro, who has taken hostages in a farm house.　　  在19世纪中叶的变革时期，有一郎离开日本西北海岸（Unasaka）的部族封地，前往遥远的江户幕府担任重要职务，他的武士朋友穆内佐（Munezo）和沙门（Samon）向他告别。穆内佐的父亲在一项桥梁工程失败后被迫自杀，此后，穆内佐一直与母亲和妹妹希诺过着简朴的生活。Kie，一个农场女孩在他们家里充当女佣。随着时间的推移，穆内佐的姐姐嫁给了萨蒙，他的母亲去世了，基嫁给了一个商人家庭，他被要求从江户派来的一名官员那里学习西方的战争方法，例如使用火炮和火器。得知基因虐待而生病，他将她从丈夫家中救出。尽管穆内佐和基伊之间有着共同的感情和尊重，但由于不同的种姓，他们仍然不可能结婚。当现在是单身汉的穆内佐因在家服侍而受到批评时，穆内佐把她送回了父亲的农场。在陷入一场失败的政治阴谋后，一郎被丢脸地遣送回国，并被单独监禁。Yaichiro逃跑后，Munezo被命令通过杀害他的老朋友来证明自己的清白，并寻求他的老老师、剑术大师Kansai Toda的帮助。虽然在他们一起学习的时候，矢一郎是一个更好的剑客，但托达只将“隐藏之刃”的秘密委托给了穆内佐。托达现在教给他一种新的技巧，让他在准备面对在农舍劫持人质的一郎时使用。

cast: Ted Levine , Kathleen Quinlan , Dan Byrd , Emilie de Ravin , Maxime Giffard , Michael Bailey Smith , Tom Bower , Aaron Stanford , Vinessa Shaw , Maisie Camilleri Preziosi , Robert Joy , Laura Ortiz , Ezra Buzzington , Billy Drago , Greg Nicotero , Ivana Turchetto , Desmond Askew , Judith Jane Vallette
summary: While celebrating their 30th wedding anniversary, a couple are traveling through the desert with their 3 children, son in law and their baby granddaughter. While the rest of the family agrees there are plenty of better and more appropriate things to do to celebrate an anniversary, they make do with what they have, but things take a turn after a sketchy gas station attendant informs them about a "short cut" that will take them in between a series of hills in the desert. It doesn't take too long before they realize they're not alone and the hills indeed do have eyes.　　  在庆祝结婚30周年之际，一对夫妇带着他们的3个孩子、女婿和他们的小孙女穿越沙漠。虽然家里其他人都同意有很多更好、更合适的事情可以做来庆祝周年纪念日，但他们还是将就着做，但在一位粗略的加油站服务员告诉他们一条“捷径”后，事情发生了转变，这条捷径将把他们带到沙漠中的一系列山丘之间。没过多久，他们就意识到自己并不孤单，群山确实有眼睛。

title: The Hills Have Eyes II (2007)
genre: 恐怖 惊悚
cast: Daniella Alonso , Jacob Vargas , Michael Bailey Smith , Cécile Breccia , Archie Kao , Jay Acovone , Jeff Kober , Philip Pavel , David Reynolds , Tyrell Kemlo , Lee Thompson Young , Eric Edelstein , Jessica Stroup , Joseph Beddelem , Ben Crowley , Michael McMillian , Reshad Strik , Fatiha Quatili
summary: A team of trainees of the National Guard brings supply to the New Mexico Desert for a group of soldiers and scientists that are installing a monitoring system in Sector 16. They do not find anybody in the camp, and they receive a blurred distress signal from the hills. Their sergeant gathers a rescue team, and they are attacked and trapped by deformed cannibals, having to fight to survive.　　  国民警卫队的一队受训人员向新墨西哥沙漠运送物资，供一群士兵和科学家在16区安装监测系统。他们在营地里找不到任何人，他们从山里收到了模糊的求救信号。他们的中士召集了一支救援队，他们遭到畸形食人族的袭击和围困，不得不为生存而战。

title: La montaña sagrada (1973)
genre: 冒险 剧情 奇幻
cast: Alejandro Jodorowsky , Horacio Salinas , Zamira Saunders , Juan Ferrara , Adriana Page , Burt Kleiner , Valerie Jodorowsky , Nicky Nichols , Richard Rutowski , Luis Lomelí , Ana De Sade , Chucho-Chucho , Letícia Robles , Connie De La Mora , David Kapralik , Jacqueline Voltaire , Pablo Leder , Bobby Cameron
summary: A Christlike figure wanders through bizarre, grotesque scenarios filled with religious and sacrilegious imagery. He meets a mystical guide who introduces him to seven wealthy and powerful people, each representing a planet in the Solar system. These seven, along with the protagonist, the guide and the guide's assistant, divest themselves of their worldly goods and form a group of nine who will seek the Holy Mountain, in order to displace the gods who live there and become immortal.　　  一个基督般的人物在充满宗教和亵渎形象的怪诞场景中徘徊。他遇到了一位神秘的向导，他把他介绍给了七位富有而有权势的人，每一位都代表着太阳系中的一颗行星。这七个人，连同主人公、向导和向导的助手，放弃了他们的世俗财产，组成了一个由九个人组成的小组，他们将寻求圣山，以取代居住在那里的神，并成为不朽的神。

title: The Holiday (2006)
genre: 喜剧 爱情
cast: Kate Winslet , Cameron Diaz , Jude Law , Jack Black , Eli Wallach , Edward Burns , Rufus Sewell , Miffy Englefield , Emma Pritchard , Sarah Parish , Shannyn Sossamon , Bill Macy , Shelley Berman , Kathryn Hahn , John Krasinski , Alex O'Loughlin , Odette Annable , Bundle Williams
summary: In London, Iris Simpkins writes a wedding column in a newspaper and nurtures an unrequited love for her colleague Jasper Bloom. Near Christmas, she is informed that Jasper is engaged to marry another colleague, and her life turns upside down. In Los Angeles, the movie-trailers maker Amanda Woods has just split with her unfaithful boyfriend Ethan and wants to forget him. Through a house exchange website, Amanda impulsively swaps her mansion for Iris' cottage in Surrey for the holidays. While in Surrey, Amanda meets Iris' brother and book editor Graham and they fall in love with each other. Meanwhile, Iris meets her new next door neighbor the ninety year old screenplay writer Arthur, who helps her retrieve her self-esteem, and the film composer Miles, with whom she falls in love.　　  在伦敦，艾丽斯·辛普金斯（Iris Simpkins）在一家报纸上写了一篇婚礼专栏，并为她的同事贾斯珀·布鲁姆（Jasper Bloom）培养了一份单恋。圣诞节临近时，她得知贾斯珀已与另一位同事订婚，她的生活发生了翻天覆地的变化。在洛杉矶，电影制作人阿曼达·伍兹（Amanda Woods）刚刚与她不忠的男友伊桑（Ethan）分手，并想忘记他。通过一家房屋交易网站，阿曼达冲动地将自己的豪宅换成了萨里郡艾丽丝的小屋，以度过假期。在萨里，阿曼达遇到了艾丽丝的哥哥兼图书编辑格雷厄姆，他们相爱了。与此同时，艾丽斯遇到了她的新邻居，90岁的剧本作家亚瑟，亚瑟帮她找回了自尊，还有电影作曲家迈尔斯，她爱上了迈尔斯。

genre: 动作 犯罪 惊悚
cast: Bill Skarsgård , Jessica Rothe , Michelle Dockery , Brett Gelman , Isaiah Mustafa , Yayan Ruhian , Cameron Crovetti , Nicholas Crovetti , Quinn Copeland , Andrew Koji , Sharlto Copley , H. Jon Benjamin , Famke Janssen , Dawid Szatarski , Dorothy Ann Gould , Rolanda Marais , Jane de Wet , Jody Abrahams
summary: Skarsgård stars as "Boy" who vows revenge after his family is murdered by Hilda Van Der Koy (Janssen), the deranged matriarch of a corrupt post-apocalyptic dynasty that left the boy orphaned, deaf, and voiceless. Driven by his inner voice, one which he co-opted from his favorite childhood video game, Boy trains with a mysterious shaman (Ruhian) to become an instrument of death and is set loose on the eve of the annual culling of dissidents. Bedlam ensues as Boy commits bloody martial arts mayhem, inciting wrath of carnage and blood-letting. As he tries to get his bearings in this delirious realm, Boy soon falls in with a desperate resistance group, all the while bickering with the apparent ghost of his rebellious little sister.　　  斯卡斯加德饰演“男孩”，在他的家人被希尔达·范·德科伊（詹森饰）谋杀后发誓复仇。希尔达·凡·德科依是一个腐败的后启示录王朝的精神错乱的女族长，这一王朝使男孩成为孤儿、聋子和哑巴。在内心声音的驱使下，男孩与一名神秘的萨满（Ruhian）一起训练，成为一种死亡工具，并在一年一度的异见分子屠杀前夕释放。疯人院接踵而至，男孩犯下了血腥的武术暴行，激起了屠杀和流血的愤怒。当他试图在这个疯狂的领域找到自己的方向时，男孩很快就陷入了一个绝望的抵抗组织，一直在与他叛逆妹妹的明显幽灵争吵。

title: Love (2015)
genre: 剧情 爱情
cast: Aomi Muyock , Karl Glusman , Klara Kristin , Juan Saavedra , Ugo Fox , Gaspar Noé , Isabelle Nicou , Benoît Debie , Vincent Maraval , Déborah Révy , Xamira Zuloaga , Stella Rocha , Omaima S. , David Bohm , Richard Blondel , Nikita Bellucci , Kelly Pix , Tony Caliano
summary: Murphy is an American cinema school student, living in Paris. He had a French girlfriend, called Electra, whom he dated for two years. One day, they met and had a no-strings-attached threesome with another woman, a young blonde Danish teenager named Omi, as a way to add some excitement to their love life. But later, he had sex with her behind Electra's back, as a result of which Omi became pregnant. This unplanned pregnancy ended the relationship between Murphy and Electra on a horrible note, and it forced Murphy to marry Omi. In one morning, Electra's mother, Nora, phones him to ask if he's heard from Electra, because she hasn't heard from her for three months, and given her daughter's suicidal tendencies. For the rest of this day, he recalls his past two years with Electra in a series of fragmented, nonlinear flashbacks; how they first met in Paris, their quick hookup, and their lives over the next two years which is filled with drug abuse, rough sex and tender moments.　　  墨菲是一名美国电影学校的学生，住在巴黎。他有一个法国女友，名叫伊莱克特拉，他和她约会了两年。一天，为了给他们的爱情生活增添一些刺激，他们遇到了另一个女人，一个年轻的丹麦金发少女，名叫Omi，并与她进行了一次不戴戒指的三人行。但后来，他在Electra的背后与她发生了性关系，结果Omi怀孕了。这场意外怀孕以一种可怕的方式结束了墨菲和伊莱克特拉之间的关系，迫使墨菲与奥米结婚。一天早上，Electra的母亲Nora打电话给他，问他是否有Electra消息，因为她已经三个月没有她的消息了，而且考虑到她女儿的自杀倾向。这一天余下的时间里，他用一系列支离破碎、非线性的倒叙回忆了他在Electra的过去两年；他们是如何在巴黎第一次见面的，他们的快速交往，以及在接下来的两年里，他们的生活充满了吸毒、粗暴性爱和温柔的时刻。

summary: A young Russian woman named Natasha is soon to be married and is on holiday in Rome where she meets Alba. summary: Campus radio star Wesley Hardin Johnson Jr., a Christmas buff in jingle bells mood at the beginning of the season, cheerfully offers to drive fellow student Megan, whose ride fell trough, home to New England and makes it an unforgettable fun voyage. title: The Texas Chainsaw Massacre
genre: 恐怖
cast: Jordana Brewster  ,  Matt Bomer  ,  Diora Baird  ,  Taylor Handley  ,  R. Lee Ermey  ,  Andrew Bryniarski  ,  Lee Tergesen  ,  Terrence Evans  ,  Kathy Lamkin  ,  Marietta Marich  ,  L.A. Calkins  ,  Tim DeZarn  ,  Allison Marich  ,  Marcus H. Nelson  ,  Lew Temple  ,  Cyia Batten  ,  Melody Chase  ,  Heather Kafka
summary: In August, 1939, a worker goes into labor while working in a slaughterhouse and dies after a complicated labor, though the deformed child survives. The possibly orphaned baby is dumped in a garbage container and found by a beggar later, who brings him home. Along the years, the mentally retarded and disturbed boy called Thomas is raised by the Hewitt family in spite of having psychological problems as well as suffering from an unnamed skin disorder, later working in a meat packing plant. In July, 1969, when the facility is closed, the inhabitants move to other places, but the deformed, mentally childlike Thomas flies into a rage after being insulted and kills the foreman. His deranged brother (considered his uncle due to their age difference) executes the sheriff that is going to arrest Thomas, and assumes his identity, wearing his clothes,driving his car though the roads in Texas and entitling himself as Sheriff Hoyt. Meanwhile, the brothers Eric and Dean are traveling in a Jeep with their girlfriends Christie and Bailey, Eric to serve in Vietnam and Dean escaping to Mexico. When the group has a car accident, Hoyt arrests Eric, Dean and Bailey and brings them to his house. Christie follows them trying to rescue the trio, trapped in the house of sadistic and insane cannibals, in a trip of horror and gore.　　  1939年8月，一名工人在屠宰场工作时临产，在一次复杂的劳动后死亡，尽管残疾儿童幸存下来。这个可能成为孤儿的婴儿被扔在垃圾桶里，后来被一个乞丐发现，并被带回家。多年来，尽管患有心理问题和一种不知名的皮肤病，但智障和精神失常的男孩托马斯（Thomas）是由休伊特家族抚养长大的，后来他在一家肉类包装厂工作。1969年7月，当工厂关闭时，居民们搬到了其他地方，但这位畸形的、像孩子一样的托马斯在受到侮辱后勃然大怒，并杀死了领班。他的精神错乱的兄弟（因年龄差异被认为是他的叔叔）处决了将要逮捕托马斯的治安官，并假冒他的身份，穿着他的衣服，开车穿过德克萨斯州的道路，自称为治安官霍伊特。与此同时，埃里克和迪恩兄弟正与女友克里斯蒂和贝利、埃里克在越南服役以及迪恩逃到墨西哥，一起乘坐吉普车旅行。当该组织发生车祸时，霍伊特逮捕了埃里克、迪恩和贝利，并将他们带到了他的家。克里斯蒂跟随他们试图营救被困在虐待狂和疯狂食人族房屋中的三人组，经历了一场恐怖和血腥的旅程。

title: Trading Places (1983)
genre: 喜剧
cast: Eddie Murphy  ,  Dan Aykroyd  ,  Ralph Bellamy  ,  Don Ameche  ,  Denholm Elliott  ,  Maurice Woods  ,  Richard D. Fisher Jr.  ,  Jim Gallagher  ,  Anthony DiSabatino  ,  Bonnie Behrend  ,  Sunnie Merrill  ,  James Newell  ,  Mary St. John  ,  Bonnie Tremena  ,  David Schwartz  ,  Tom Degidon  ,  William Magerman  ,  Alan Dellay
summary: Louis Winthorpe is a businessman who works for commodities brokerage firm of Duke and Duke owned by the brothers Mortimer and Randolph Duke. Now they bicker over the most trivial of matters and what they are bickering about is whether it's a person's environment or heredity that determines how well they will do in life. When Winthorpe bumps into Billy Ray Valentine, a street hustler and assumes he is trying to rob him, he has him arrested. Upon seeing how different the two men are, the brothers decide to make a wager as to what would happen if Winthorpe loses his job, his home and is shunned by everyone he knows and if Valentine was given Winthorpe's job. So they proceed to have Winthorpe arrested and to be placed in a compromising position in front of his girlfriend. So all he has to rely on is the hooker who was hired to ruin him.　　  路易斯·温索普（Louis Winthorpe）是一名商人，为莫蒂默（Mortimer）和伦道夫·杜克（Randolph Duke）兄弟所属的杜克和杜克（Duke）大宗商品经纪公司工作。现在，他们为最琐碎的事情争吵不休，他们争论的是，是一个人的环境还是遗传决定了他们生活的好坏。当温索普遇到街头骗子比利·雷·瓦伦丁（Billy Ray Valentine）并以为他要抢劫时，他将其逮捕。看到这两个人有多么不同，兄弟俩决定打赌，如果温索普失去工作，失去家园，被他认识的每个人都回避，如果瓦伦丁得到温索普的工作，会发生什么。因此，他们着手逮捕了温索普，并在他的女友面前摆出妥协的姿态。所以他所依赖的就是那个雇来毁掉他的妓女。

title: Nosferatu, eine Symphonie des Grauens (1922)
genre: 奇幻 恐怖
cast: Max Schreck  ,  Alexander Granach  ,  Gustav von Wangenheim  ,  Greta Schröder  ,  Georg H. Schnell  ,  Ruth Landshoff  ,  Gustav Botz  ,  John Gottowt  ,  Max Nemetz  ,  Wolfgang Heinz  ,  Albert Venohr  ,  Karl Etlinger  ,  Hans Lanser-Ludolff  ,  Loni Nest  ,  Fritz Rasp  ,  Josef Sareny  ,  Fanny Schreck  ,  Eric van Viele
summary: Wisbourg, Germany based estate agent Knock dispatches his associate, Hutter, to Count Orlok's castle in Transylvania as the Count wants to purchase an isolated house in Wisbourg. They plan on selling him the one across the way from Hutter's own home. Hutter leaves his innocent wife, Ellen, with some friends while he is away. Hutter's trek is an unusual one, with many locals not wanting to take him near the castle where strange events have been occurring. Once at the castle, Hutter does manage to sell the Count the house, but he also notices and feels unusual occurrences, primarily feeling like there is a dark shadow hanging over him, even in the daytime when the Count is unusually asleep. Hutter eventually sees the Count's sleeping chamber in a crypt, and based on a book he has recently read, believes the Count is really a vampire or Nosferatu. While Hutter is trapped in the castle, the Count, hiding in a shipment of coffins, makes his way to Wisbourg, causing death along his way, which most attribute to the plague. Hutter himself tries to rush home to save his town and most importantly save Ellen from Nosferatu's imminent arrival. In Wisbourg, Ellen can feel the impending darkness as Nosferatu gets closer. But she learns that a sinless woman can sacrifice herself to kill the vampire. Will Hutter be able to save Ellen either from Nosferatu and/or her self-sacrifice?　　  德国房地产经纪人诺克（Knock）派遣助手赫特（Hutter）前往特兰西瓦尼亚（Transylvania）奥洛克伯爵（Count Orlok）的城堡，因为伯爵想在威斯堡（Wisbourg）购买一栋与世隔绝的房子。他们计划把赫特家对面的房子卖给他。赫特离开时，把他无辜的妻子艾伦留给了一些朋友。赫特的徒步旅行很不寻常，许多当地人不想带他去发生奇怪事件的城堡附近。在城堡里，赫特确实成功地把房子卖给了伯爵，但他也注意到并感觉到了一些不寻常的事情，主要是觉得有一个黑暗的阴影笼罩着他，即使是在伯爵异常熟睡的白天。赫特最终在一个地窖里看到了伯爵的卧房，根据他最近读到的一本书，他相信伯爵真的是一个吸血鬼或Nosferatu。当赫特被困在城堡中时，伯爵躲藏在一批棺材中，前往威斯堡，途中造成死亡，这主要归因于瘟疫。赫特自己也试图赶回家来拯救他的小镇，最重要的是，他要把埃伦从即将到来的诺斯费拉图手中救出来。在威斯堡，埃伦可以感受到随着诺斯费拉图越来越近，即将到来的黑暗。但她知道一个无罪的女人可以牺牲自己来杀死吸血鬼。Hutter能从Nosferatu和/或她的自我牺牲中拯救Ellen吗？

title: The Boys in the Boat (2023)
genre: 传记 剧情 运动
cast: Joel Edgerton , Callum Turner , Peter Guinness , Sam Strike , Thomas Elms , Jack Mulhern , Luke Slattery , Bruce Herbelin-Earle , Wil Coban , Tom Varey , Joel Phillimore , James Wolk , Hadley Robinson , Courtney Henggeler , Chris Diamantopoulos , Glenn Wrage , Edward Baker-Duly , Adrian Lukis
summary: The Boys in the Boat is a sports drama based on the #1 New York Times bestselling non-fiction novel written by Daniel James Brown. title: Mang gwai chai goon (1987)
genre: 动作 喜剧 恐怖
cast: Jacky Cheung , Ricky Hui , Kitty Chan , Fung Woo , Billy Lau , Rico Chu , Fat Chung , Yin Szema , Fung Ging-Man , Kim-Wan Chan , Lee-Lee Lau , Yeung-Do Lee , Ho-Kwan Lee , Tsun-Hung Liu , Yin Chi , Biu Gam , Ching Wai , King-Fan Lee
summary: A Hong Kong police station used to be a clubhouse of the Japanese at the time of their occupation of the city during World War II. However, at the end of the war, many of the Japanese committed haka kiri in the clubhouse. In the present time, after thief Sneaky Ming (Billy Lau) was captured and incarcerated at the station, he was lured into a world of the paranormal by the spirits of those still inhabiting the building. He was tricked into unleashing the fierce General Issei (Rico Chu), who resurrects into a vampire and wreaks havoc in the city. As a result, police officers Kam Mark-K (Jacky Cheung) and Man-Chill (Ricky Hui) attempt to put a stop to the terror.　　  第二次世界大战期间，日本人占领香港时，香港一家警察局曾是日本人的俱乐部。然而，在战争结束时，许多日本人在俱乐部会所举行了哈卡舞。目前，小偷Sneaky Ming（Billy Lau饰）在车站被抓获并监禁后，他被仍居住在大楼里的人们的灵魂引诱进入了一个超自然的世界。他被骗释放了凶猛的伊赛将军（朱棣文饰），伊赛将军复活为吸血鬼，在城市中制造了巨大破坏。因此，警察Kam Mark-K（张学友饰）和Man-Chill（许瑞琪饰）试图阻止恐怖活动。

summary: A remake of the classic 1963 movie "The Haunting" about a team of paranormal experts who look into strange occurrences in an ill-fated house. Through the course of the night some will unravel, some will question, and all will fight for their lives as the house fights back.　　  这是对1963年经典电影《幽灵》的翻拍，讲述了一组超自然专家在一所命运多舛的房子里调查奇怪事件的故事。在整个夜晚，一些人会被拆散，一些人将提出质疑，所有人都会为自己的生命而战，因为房子会反击。

title: The Boynton Beach Bereavement Club (2005)
genre: 喜剧 爱情
cast: Dyan Cannon , Joseph Bologna , Brenda Vaccaro , Len Cariou , Sally Kellerman , Michael Nouri , Renée Taylor , Mal Z. Lawrence , Ashley Blackwell , Kim Ostrenko , Janice Hamilton , Irene B. Colletti , Barbara Pergament , Loli Rainey , George Schiavone , Alden McKay , Damaris Justamante , Jody Wilson
summary: A romantic comedy about our amazing capacity to rebound and fall in love at any age. Lois, Harry, Marilyn ,Sandy and Jack live in an "Active Adult" community in Boynton Beach, Florida. Their lives intersect when they meet at a local Bereavement Club where they go to find emotional support after the loss of a loved one. For anyone who thinks that new love and romance ends long before retirement, they're in for a reality check. No one sees themselves as becoming old, and the residents of Boynton Beach aren't about to start. But sometimes we all need a little reminder that life is worth living and sharing.　　  这是一部浪漫喜剧，讲述了我们在任何年龄段都有惊人的反弹和坠入爱河的能力。路易斯、哈里、玛丽莲、桑迪和杰克住在佛罗里达州博因顿海滩的一个“活跃成年人”社区。当他们在当地的丧亲俱乐部见面时，他们的生活发生了交叉，在失去亲人后，他们会去那里寻求情感支持。对于那些认为新的爱情和浪漫会在退休前很久就结束的人来说，他们是在接受现实检验。没有人认为自己会变老，博因顿海滩的居民也不会开始变老。但有时，我们都需要一个小小的提醒，即生活是值得生活和分享的。

summary: Three students from Jing Mu Girls' Middle School go missing and turn up dead. Xiao Tong, a special education student with speech impairment, feels like someone is watching her. During the rehearsal for the school's foundation day event, a corpse falls from the ceiling of the auditorium, and Xiao Tong disappears in the midst of confusion. Her mother, Li Han, who has been working at the school to be close to Xiao Tong, begins her pursuit.　　  荆木女子中学的三名学生失踪并死亡。小童是一名患有语言障碍的特殊教育学生，她觉得有人在看着她。在学校成立日活动的排练过程中，一具尸体从礼堂的天花板上掉了下来，小童在混乱中消失了。她的母亲李涵（音）一直在学校工作，与小童关系密切，她开始了她的追求。

genre: 犯罪 剧情 悬疑
cast: Tom Bateman , Annette Bening , Kenneth Branagh , Russell Brand , Michael Rouse , Alaa Safi , Orlando Seale , Charlie Anson , Danny Hughes , Sam James Page , James Schofield , George Jaques , Jonah Rzeskiewicz , Eleanor de Rohan , Susannah Fielding , Adam Garcia , Rick Warden , Noel White
summary: Belgian sleuth Hercule Poirot's vacation aboard a glamorous river steamer turns into a terrifying search for a murderer when a picture-perfect couple's idyllic honeymoon is tragically cut short. Set against an epic landscape of sweeping Egyptian desert vistas and the majestic Giza pyramids, this tale of unbridled passion and incapacitating jealousy features a cosmopolitan group of impeccably dressed travelers, and enough wicked twists and turns to leave audiences guessing until the final, shocking denouement.　　  比利时侦探赫尔克里·波洛（Hercule Poirot）乘坐一艘迷人的内河轮船度假，当一对风景如画的情侣的田园诗般的蜜月被不幸地缩短时，他开始可怕地寻找凶手。与横扫埃及沙漠的壮丽景色和雄伟的吉萨金字塔形成对比的是，这部讲述激情奔放和嫉妒无能为力的故事，主角是一群衣着无可挑剔的旅行者，以及足以让观众猜到最后令人震惊的结局的邪恶曲折。

title: Entrapment (1999)
genre: 动作 犯罪 爱情
cast: Sean Connery , Catherine Zeta-Jones , Ving Rhames , Will Patton , Maury Chaykin , Kevin McNally , Terry O'Neill , Madhav Sharma , David Yip , Tim Potter , Eric Meyers , Aaron Swartz , William Marsh , Tony Xu , Rolf Saxon , Tom Clarke Hill , David Howard , Stuart Ong
summary: Following the theft of a highly-secured piece of artwork, an agent convinces her insurance agency employers to allow her to wriggle into the company of an aging but active master thief. Connery's burglar takes her on suspiciously and demands rigorous training before their first job together, stealing a highly-valued mask from a chichi party. Their deepening attraction and distrust could tear apart their partnership, but the promise of a bigger prize (some eight billion odd dollars) by Zeta-Jones keeps the game interesting. Only, who's playing with whom?　　  在一件高度固化的艺术品被盗后，一名经纪人说服她的保险公司雇主允许她潜入一名年迈但活跃的盗贼老爷的公司。康纳利的窃贼带着她的疑心，要求在他们第一次合作之前接受严格的培训，从一个奇奇派对上偷了一个价值很高的面具。他们日益加深的吸引力和不信任可能会破坏他们的合作关系，但齐塔-琼斯（Zeta-Jones）承诺的更大奖金（约80多亿美元）让游戏变得有趣。只是，谁在和谁玩？

title: Fukudamura Jiken (2023)
genre: 剧情 历史 惊悚
cast: Koshi Misaki , Yuka Kouri , Airi Aoki , Akira Emoto , Suidôbashi Hakase , Sara Hayama , Masahiro Higashide , Kom I. , Arata Iura , Miki Kanai , Shinsuke Kato , Mai Kiryû , Yûya Matsuura , Eita Nagayama , Gorô Satô , Rairu Sugita , Pierre Taki , Rena Tanaka
summary: In 1923, Tomokazu Sawada left Gyojo (present-day Seoul) under Japanese rule, where he was a teacher, and returned to his hometown, Fukuda Village, Chiba Prefecture, with his wife Shizuko. Sawada was a witness to the massacre committed by the Japanese army in Korea, but he hid that fact from Shizuko as well. On September 1st of that year, a big earthquake hit the Kanto region. On September 6, when many people were in chaos and rumors were flying, a group of 15 peddlers led by Shinsuke Numabe, who had come from Kagawa to Kanto, headed to the Tone River ferry to head to their next destination. A misunderstanding that began as a small argument between Numabe and the ferryman ignited the collective psychology of the excited villagers, resulting in a massacre that would later be buried in history.　　  1923年，佐田友子（Tomokazu Sawada）离开日本统治下的Gyojo（现在的首尔），在那里他是一名教师，与妻子静子（Shizuko）一起回到了家乡千叶县福田村。泽田是日军在朝鲜大屠杀的目击者，但他也向静子隐瞒了这一事实。那年9月1日，一场大地震袭击了关东地区。9月6日，当许多人陷入混乱，谣言四处传播时，由Shinsuke Numabe率领的15名小贩从卡加瓦前往关东，前往Tone River渡轮，前往下一个目的地。努马贝和渡船人之间的一场小争吵引发了一场误解，点燃了兴奋的村民们的集体心理，导致了一场屠杀，这场屠杀后来将被埋葬在历史长河中。

title: Ashita wo Tsuzuru Shashinkan (2024)
genre: 剧情
cast: Hidekazu Akai , Miyu Hayashida , Sei Hiraizumi , Yoshie Ichige , Riku Kashima , Michiko Kichise , Hitomi Kuroki , Jun Miho , Masaya Sano , Kôichi Satô , Katsunori Takahashi , Ken Tanaka , Koki Tanaka
summary: Takeharu Samejima is a reticent photographer who runs a deserted photo studio. Taiichi Igarashi, a talented photographer captivated by his photos, gives up his brilliant career to become his apprentice. Taiichi, who has even avoided communication with his family, cannot hide his surprise at Takeharu's deep involvement with clients, engaging in thoughtful conversations that transcend the typical photographer-subject relationship. While tossed around by Takeharu's desperate efforts to address people's troubles and problems, Taiichi realizes what he lacks. At the same time, he learns that Takeharu and his family also have their own regrets that they've been avoiding. Taiichi is changing and taking a step forward for a future without regrets.　　  Takeharu Samejima是一位沉默寡言的摄影师，他经营着一家废弃的摄影棚。井石良一，一位被照片迷住的天才摄影师，放弃了辉煌的职业生涯，成为了他的徒弟。Taiichi甚至避免与家人沟通，他无法掩饰自己对武原与客户深入接触的惊讶，他参与了超越典型摄影师-主体关系的深思熟虑的对话。当武原竭尽全力解决人们的麻烦和问题时，太一意识到了自己的不足。与此同时，他了解到武林和他的家人也有他们自己一直在回避的遗憾。Taiichi正在改变，朝着无悔的未来迈进了一步。

summary: A cat belonging to a poor miller's son thinks up a great plan for bringing a title, wealth, and marriage for his owner. He begins to carry it out, using a few birds and rabbits as gifts for the king, his own wit, and a pair of boots that make him appear human when he puts them on. However, his owner has no idea that the cat has told everyone that his master is a marquis rather than a miller's son until the king has arrived to meet him. Soon the king's daughter and the miller's son fall in love, and the king wants very much to see the land and the castle belonging to this rich "marquis."　　  一只属于一个贫穷磨坊主儿子的猫想出了一个伟大的计划，为主人带来头衔、财富和婚姻。他开始这样做，用几只鸟和几只兔子作为礼物送给国王，用他自己的智慧和一双靴子，当他穿上靴子时，这双靴子使他看起来像人。然而，在国王来见他之前，他的主人并不知道这只猫已经告诉大家，他的主人是侯爵，而不是磨坊主的儿子。很快，国王的女儿和磨坊主的儿子坠入爱河，国王非常想看到这位富有的“侯爵”的土地和城堡

summary: Detective Virgil Tibbs is caught up in the racial tension of the US South when he is arrested after the murder of a prominent businessman. Tibbs was simply waiting for his next train at the station in Sparta, Mississippi and the confusion is soon resolved but when local police chief Gillespie learns that Tibbs is the Philadelphia PD's number one homicide expert, he reluctantly asks for his assistance. The murdered man, Mr. Colbert, had come to Sparta from the North to build a new factory and his wife and business associates immediately point the finger at Endicott, the most powerful man in the county and the one who had the most to lose if a major new employer comes to the area. Tibbs' life is clearly in danger but he perseveres in a highly charged and racially explosive environment until the killer is found.　　  侦探维吉尔·蒂布斯（Virgil Tibbs）因谋杀一名著名商人而被捕，他陷入了美国南部的种族紧张局势。蒂布斯当时只是在密西西比州斯巴达车站等下一班火车，混乱很快就解决了，但当当地警察局长吉莱斯皮得知蒂布斯是费城警察局的头号杀人专家时，他很不情愿地请求协助。被谋杀的男子科尔伯特先生从北方来到斯巴达建造一家新工厂，他的妻子和商业伙伴立即将矛头指向恩迪科特，他是该县最有权势的人，也是该地区新雇主到来时损失最大的人。蒂布斯的生命显然处于危险之中，但他坚持在充满激情和种族爆炸的环境中，直到凶手被找到。

summary: In 1928, in Egypt, a strange device is found by an expedition. In the present days, the outcast linguist Dr. Daniel Jackson is invited by a mysterious woman to decipher an ancient hieroglyph in a military facility. Soon he finds that the device was developed by an advanced civilization and opens a portal to teletransport to another planet. Dr. Jackson is invited to join a military team under the command of Colonel Jonathan 'Jack' O'Neil that will explore the new world. They find a land that recalls Egypt and humans in a primitive culture that worship and are slaves to Ra, the God of the Sun. But soon they discover the secret of the mysterious "stargate".　　  1928年，在埃及，一支探险队发现了一个奇怪的装置。如今，被驱逐的语言学家丹尼尔·杰克逊博士受到一位神秘女子的邀请，在军事设施中破译一个古代象形文字。很快，他发现该设备是由一个先进文明开发的，并打开了通往另一个星球的远程传输门户。杰克逊博士被邀请加入一支由乔纳森·杰克·奥尼尔上校指挥的军事团队，该团队将探索新世界。他们发现这片土地让人想起埃及和原始文化中的人类，他们崇拜太阳神Ra，并成为其奴隶。但很快他们就发现了神秘的“星际之门”的秘密。

summary: Journalist Jenny Lerner is assigned to look into the background of Secretary Alan Rittenhouse who abruptly resigned from government citing his wife's ill health. She learns from his secretary that Rittenhouse was having an affair with someone named Ellie but when she confronts him, his strange reaction leads her to reconsider her story. In fact, a comet, discovered the previous year by high school student Leo Biederman and astronomer Dr. Marcus Wolf, is on a collision course with the Earth, an Extinction Level Event. A joint US-Russian team is sent to destroy the comet but should it fail, special measures are to be put in place to secure the future of mankind. As the space mission progresses, many individuals deal with their fears and ponder their future.　　  记者珍妮·勒纳（Jenny Lerner）被指派调查国务卿艾伦·里滕豪斯（Alan Rittenhouse）的背景，他以妻子健康状况不佳为由突然辞职。她从他的秘书那里得知，里顿豪斯和一个叫埃莉的人有外遇，但当她面对他时，他的奇怪反应使她重新考虑了她的故事。事实上，高中生利奥·比德曼（Leo Biederman）和天文学家马库斯·沃尔夫（Marcus Wolf）博士在前一年发现的一颗彗星正在与地球发生碰撞，这是一次灭绝级事件。一个美苏联合小组被派去摧毁这颗彗星，但如果它失败了，将采取特别措施来保障人类的未来。随着太空任务的进展，许多人克服了恐惧，思考了自己的未来。

title: Bu Neng Shuo De. Mi Mi (2007)
genre: 剧情 音乐 爱情
cast: Jay Chou , Lun-Mei Gwei , Anthony Chau-Sang Wong , Ming-Ming Su , Devon Song , Kai-Syuan Tzeng , Jun Lang Huang , Yuri Chan , Chase Chang , Funky Tu , Yuki Huang , Aviis Zhong , Alex Wu , Michael Lin , Yiao-Tzong Chou , Hsun-Wei David Chang , Michael Boyen , Kuei-Giu Kong
summary: Ye Xiang Lun is a music student majoring in piano who just transferred to Tamkang, a school famous for its musically-talented students, especially those who play piano. On his first day of school, he hears a mysterious melody being played; following it, he meets Lu Xiao Yu, another piano major. When he asks her about the song she was playing, she tells him that it is a secret that cannot be told. The two form a friendship that quickly evolves into a romantic relationship. However, there is more to Xiao Yu than initially meets the eye of Ye Xiang Lun.　　  叶向伦（Ye Xiang Lun）是一名主修钢琴的音乐专业学生，他刚转学到谭康（Tamkang），这所学校以音乐天赋学生，尤其是钢琴演奏学生而闻名。在他上学的第一天，他听到一段神秘的旋律在演奏；随后，他遇到了另一位钢琴专业的陆小余。当他问起她正在演奏的歌曲时，她告诉他这是一个无法透露的秘密。两人形成了友谊，并迅速发展成为浪漫的关系。然而，小余的经历远不止叶香伦最初看到的那样。

title: Nordsjøen (2021)
genre: 动作 剧情 惊悚
cast: Kristine Kujath Thorp , Henrik Bjelland , Rolf Kristian Larsen , Anders Baasmo , Bjørn Floberg , Anneke von der Lippe , Christoffer Staib , Ane Skumsvoll , Cengiz Al , Nils Elias Olsen , Monique Amado , Daniel Frikstad , Camilla Gullbrekken , Halfdan Hallseth , Renate Hellerud , Jean-Luc Julien , Karina Knight , Hibba Najeeb
summary: In 1969, the Norwegian government announces their discovery of one of the world's largest oil fields in the neighboring North Sea, launching a prosperous period of offshore drilling. 50 years later, the environmental consequences begin to manifest - a crack has opened on the ocean floor, causing a rig to collapse. A team of researchers, including submarine operator Sofia, rushes in to search for the missing and assess the cause of the damage, but what they discover is that this is just the start of a possible apocalyptic catastrophe. As rigs are evacuated, Sofia's loving companion Stian becomes trapped in the depths of the sea, and Sofia must dive in to rescue him. THE BURNING SEA is the latest disaster epic from the team behind Skjelvet (2018) and Bølgen (2015).　　  1969年，挪威政府宣布在邻近的北海发现了世界上最大的油田之一，开启了海上钻井的繁荣时期。50年后，环境后果开始显现，海底出现裂缝，导致钻井平台坍塌。包括潜艇运营商索菲亚（Sofia）在内的一组研究人员赶来寻找失踪人员，并评估造成损害的原因，但他们发现，这只是一场可能的世界末日灾难的开始。随着钻井平台的撤离，索菲亚的挚友斯迪安被困在深海中，索菲娅必须潜入水中营救他。《燃烧的海洋》是斯科耶夫特（2018）和博根（2015）团队最新推出的灾难史诗。

title: Ye kong que (2015)
genre: 剧情 爱情
cast: Yifei Liu , Leon Lai , Ye Liu , Shaoqun Yu , Emmanuel Gayet , Florian Delpech , Jonathan Louis
summary: Elsa, a Chinese musician born in France, travels to Chengdu for work. There she meets silk scholar Rong who also plays the flute. Through his music, she falls in love with the middle-aged widower. Together they unlock the long-lost secret that Song Dynasty silk was made by a rare silkworm, the Night Peacock. Rong's son Xiaolin, who plays female roles in Sichuan Opera, has a psychotic breakdown after spying her having sex with his father. Burdened with guilt, Elsa flees to Paris only to enter into a relationship with Rong's brother, Jianming, who tattoos the image of the Night Peacock moth on her back. Elsa finally decides to keep the baby only to learn that she is pregnant with his Rong's child. The Night Peacock has one final aria to sing.　　  埃尔莎是一位出生于法国的中国音乐家，她来到成都工作。在那里，她遇到了同样会吹长笛的丝绸学者荣。通过他的音乐，她爱上了这位中年鳏夫。他们一起揭开了一个失传已久的秘密：宋代丝绸是由一种罕见的蚕——夜孔雀制成的。荣的儿子小林在川剧中扮演女性角色，在看到她与父亲发生性关系后，精神崩溃。艾尔莎负债累累，逃到巴黎，却与荣的哥哥建明（Jianming）发生了关系，建明在她背上纹了夜孔雀蛾的形象。艾尔莎最终决定留下孩子，只是为了知道自己怀上了荣的孩子。《夜孔雀》还有最后一首咏叹调要唱。

summary: Jackie Chan's Hong Kong variation of Frank Capra's "A Pocketful of Miracles" set in the 1930s. Jackie plays a country boy who rescues a gang boss. Jackie becomes the head of a gang through the purchase of some lucky roses from an old lady. title: The Gunman (2015)
genre: 动作 犯罪 悬疑
cast: Sean Penn , Idris Elba , Jasmine Trinca , Javier Bardem , Ray Winstone , Mark Rylance , Peter Franzén , Mark Billingham , Daniel Adegboyega , Ade Oyefeso , Alejandro Talavante , Florian Barisey , Ismael Tunkara , Amara Tunkara , Rachel Lascar , Miquel Àngel Ripeu , Mark Schardan , Txiki Blasi
summary: A sniper on a mercenary assassination team, working for an unknown client, kills the minister of mines of the Congo. Terrier's (Sean Penn's) successful kill shot forces him to go into hiding to protect himself and the members of the team from retribution. This includes abruptly abandoning his girlfriend who has no idea what is going on. The assassination, paid for by a foreign mining company, triggers wide spread chaos and death in an already inflamed Congo. Terrier returns to the Congo years later working for an NGO, but eventually finds that he's the target of a paid hit squad somehow connected to the minister's assassination. This leads to immediate deaths and the endangerment of the people working around him, and forces him back into hiding. In trying to discover who has put a price on his head, he begins to reconnect to the members of his old assassination team, including his old girlfriend. Always aware that there is no path to redemption for his crimes, he is also periodically incapacitated by a type of accumulated and evolving physical brain damage caused by the hard knocks of his occupation. Unexpectedly, given the time that has elapsed, his reconnection to his old assassination team exposes additional intrigues with immediate deadly consequences. All of his years spent in hiding, have merely delayed the twisted end game that now enfolds.　　  一名雇佣兵暗杀小组的狙击手为一名身份不明的客户工作，杀害了刚果矿业部长。特里尔（肖恩·佩恩饰）的成功射杀迫使他躲藏起来，以保护自己和队员免受惩罚。这包括突然抛弃他不知道发生了什么事的女友。这起由一家外国矿业公司出资的暗杀事件，在一个已经火上浇油的刚果引发了广泛的混乱和死亡。几年后，特里尔回到了刚果，为一家非政府组织工作，但最终发现，他是一支有偿暗杀小组的目标，该小组与这位部长的暗杀有某种联系。这导致了他周围工作人员的立即死亡和危险，迫使他重新躲藏起来。为了找出是谁给他的头定了价，他开始与包括他的前女友在内的旧暗杀小组成员重新联系。他始终意识到自己的罪行是无路可走的，他也会因职业生涯中的重重打击所造成的一种不断累积和演变的脑损伤而周期性地丧失能力。出乎意料的是，考虑到时间的流逝，他与旧暗杀团队的重新联系暴露了更多的阴谋，并立即造成致命后果。他在隐藏中度过的所有岁月，只不过是推迟了现在正在上演的扭曲结局。

genre: 剧情 爱情 惊悚
cast: Kim Min-hee , Ha Jung-woo , Cho Jin-woong , Moon So-ri , Kim Tae-ri , Lee Yong-nyeo , Yoo Min-chae , Lee Dong-hwi , Kim Hae-sook , Lee Kyu-jung , Kim Si-eun , Ha Si-yeon , Rina Takagi , Won Geun-hee , Kim Jong-dae , Jang Han-sun , Kim Eun-yeong , Kim Ri-woo
summary: 1930s Korea, in the period of Japanese occupation, a new girl (Sookee) is hired as a handmaiden to a Japanese heiress (Hideko) who lives a secluded life on a large countryside estate with her domineering Uncle (Kouzuki). But the maid has a secret. She is a pickpocket recruited by a swindler posing as a Japanese Count to help him seduce the Lady to elope with him, rob her of her fortune, and lock her up in a madhouse. The plan seems to proceed according to plan until Sookee and Hideko discover some unexpected emotions.　　  20世纪30年代的韩国，在日本占领期间，一名新女孩（Sookee）被雇为日本女继承人（Hideko）的侍女，她与霸道的叔叔（Kouzuki）在一大片乡村庄园中过着隐居生活。但是女佣有一个秘密。她是一个扒手，被一个冒充日本伯爵的骗子招募来帮助他引诱这位女士与他私奔，抢走她的财产，并将她关在疯人院。计划似乎按照计划进行，直到苏基和希德科发现一些意想不到的情绪。

title: The Great Raid (2005)
genre: 动作 剧情 战争
cast: Benjamin Bratt , Joseph Fiennes , James Franco , Robert Mammone , Max Martini , James Carpinello , Mark Consuelos , Craig McLachlan , Freddie Joe Farnsworth , Laird Macintosh , Jeremy Callaghan , Scott McLean , Paolo Montalban , Clayne Crawford , Sam Worthington , Royston Innes , Diarmid Heidenreich , Luke Pegler
summary: Set in the Philippines in 1945 towards the end of WWII, under the command of Lieutenant Colonel Henry Mucci and Captain Robert Prince, the 6th Ranger Battalion undertake a daring rescue mission against all odds. Traveling thirty miles behind enemy lines, they intend to liberate over 500 American Soldiers from the notorious Cabanatuan Japanese POW camp in the most audacious rescue ever.　　  1945年二战即将结束时，第六骑兵营在亨利·穆奇中校和罗伯特·普林斯上尉的指挥下，在菲律宾展开了一次大胆的救援任务。他们在敌后30英里处行进，打算将500多名美国士兵从臭名昭著的Cabanatuan日本战俘营中解放出来，这是有史以来最大胆的营救行动。

title: Pardes (1997)
genre: 剧情 歌舞 爱情
cast: Shah Rukh Khan , Mahima Chaudhry , Amrish Puri , Apurva Agnihotri , Alok Nath , Himani Shivpuri , Padmavati Rao , Madhuri Bhatia , Dina Pathak , Benu Kalsi , Smita Jaykar , Pawan Malhotra , Rakesh Thareja , Ajay Nagrath , Aditya Narayan , Samta Sagar , Prachi Save , Deepak Qazir
summary: This film takes a serious look at the lives of Westernized Non-Resident Indians (NRIs) in North America (Whereas Dilwale Dulhania Le Jayenge was about NRIs with Indian hearts, Pardes is about Westernized NRIs.) and hence the meaning of the title - "foreign land". Kishorilal is a successful businessman settled in America but still emotionally attached to his motherland - India. So the pardesi comes to India with his "American" son Rajiv to find a suitable '"Indian" girl for him. Kishorilal hopes his soon-to-be daughter in law will instill some Indian values in his extremely westernized son. He finds his daughter in law in Kusum Ganga (a pet Subhash Ghai name just as Chandni was Yash Chopra's favorite for a long time) in the house of his childhood friend Suraj Dev. Mahima Chaudhary makes her debut as Ganga. To finalize the marriage he sends his son along with his foster son Arjun to India. Arjun plays Cupid and returns to America with Kusum and Rajiv. Arjun comes into the movie to get the American-boy to accept Indian values, and support the Indian-girl to accept American vices. The reverse does not fit into this movie. Arjun is portrayed as an Indian at heart and the hero of the film! All is hunky-dory till the true Bharatiya Nari finds out that her future husband is not a teetotaler. So, the heartbroken Kusum returns to India. Don't conclude that it is the end of the Bollywood fairy tale. It is just the beginning as Arjun falls in love with his would-have-been bhabhi while playing Cupid and leads to a love triangle.　　  这部电影严肃地审视了西方化的非居住印第安人（NRI）在北美的生活（Dilwale Dulhania Le Jayenge讲述的是印度人心中的NRI，Pardes讲述的则是西方化的NRI），因此标题的含义是“外国土地”。基什里拉尔是一位在美国定居的成功商人，但他仍然对自己的祖国印度怀有感情。所以帕德西带着他的“美国”儿子拉吉夫来到印度，为他找一个合适的“印度”女孩。基什里拉尔希望他即将成为女婿的女儿能给他极端西化的儿子灌输一些印度价值观。他在儿时好友苏拉杰·德夫·马希马·乔杜里（Suraj Dev.Mahima Chaudhary）的家中发现了他的女婿在库苏姆·甘加（Kusum Gaga）（一个叫苏巴什·甘加（Subhash Ghai）的宠物名字，就像钱德尼（Chandni）是亚斯·乔普拉（Yash Chopra）长期以来最喜欢的名字一样）。为了敲定婚姻，他把儿子和养子阿琼一起送到印度。阿琼扮演丘比特，与库苏姆和拉吉夫一起返回美国。阿琼走进电影是为了让美国男孩接受印度的价值观，并支持印度女孩接受美国的恶习。相反的情况不适合这部电影。阿琼被描绘成一个内心深处的印度人和电影中的英雄！直到真正的巴拉蒂亚·纳里发现她未来的丈夫并不是一个禁酒主义者，一切都是虚构的。于是，心碎的库苏姆回到了印度。不要认为这是宝莱坞童话的结局。这仅仅是一个开始，因为阿琼在扮演丘比特的时候爱上了他的准妈妈巴比，导致了一场三角恋。

title: The Greatest Game Ever Played (2005)
genre: 传记 剧情 运动
cast: Shia LaBeouf , Stephen Dillane , Elias Koteas , James Paxton , Tom Rack , Armand Laroche , Peter Hurley , Gregory Terlecki , Jonathan Higgins , Matthew Knight , Luke Askew , Amanda Tilson , Jamie Merling , Eugenio Esposito , Marnie McPhail , Robin Wilcock , Peter Firth , Michael Sinelnikoff
summary: Near the turn of the twentieth century, young Harry Vardon becomes a champion golfer but learns that his amazing skill is no match for the class boundaries that exclude him from "gentlemanly" English society. A dozen years later, a young American, Francis Ouimet, fights against the same prejudice, as well as his own father's disdain, for a chance to participate in the U.S. Open against his idol -- Harry Vardon. The struggles of both men for acceptance provides the background for an amazing contest of skills.　　  在20世纪末，年轻的哈里·瓦登（Harry Vardon）成为了一名高尔夫冠军，但他知道，他的惊人技能无法与将他排除在“绅士”英国社会之外的阶级界限相匹敌。十几年后，一位年轻的美国人弗朗西斯·乌伊梅特（Francis Ouimet）与同样的偏见以及他父亲的蔑视作斗争，他希望有机会与他的偶像哈里·瓦登（Harry Vardon）一起参加美国网球公开赛。这两个人为被接受而进行的斗争为一场惊人的技能竞赛提供了背景。

genre: 恐怖 惊悚
cast: Megan Fox , Eoin Macken , Callan Mulvey , Jack Roth , Aml Ameen , Stefanie Yunger , Julian Balahurov , Teodora Djuric , Lili Rich
summary: Emma is stuck in a stale marriage to Mark and is surprised when he whisks her away to their secluded lakehouse for a romantic evening on their 11th anniversary. But everything changes the next morning when she finds herself handcuffed to Mark's dead body. Trapped and isolated in the dead of winter, for Emma to survive, she must fight the mysterious killers coming to finish her off.　　  艾玛陷入了与马克陈旧的婚姻中，当马克在他们11周年纪念日那天带她去他们僻静的湖边小屋度过一个浪漫的夜晚时，她感到很惊讶。但第二天早上，当她发现自己被铐在马克的尸体上时，一切都改变了。艾玛在严冬中被困和孤立，为了生存，她必须与前来追杀她的神秘杀手搏斗。

summary: M Night Shyamalan's The Village revolves around a desolate town in Pennsylvania. The residents of this town live by strict rules - They are not to leave the village or the monsters beyond their boundaries will surely attack them. Lucius and Ivy have an attraction - a strong one. But when Noah - a man with an intellectual disability and who also has feelings for Ivy, finds out that the two are In love, Noah attacks Lucius. He will die if brave Ivy (who is blind) does not breach the borders and find help to save Lucius.　　  M Night Shyamalan的《村庄》围绕着宾夕法尼亚州的一个荒凉小镇展开。这个城镇的居民严格遵守规定——他们不能离开村庄，否则他们边界以外的怪物肯定会袭击他们。卢修斯和常春藤有一种吸引力——一种强烈的吸引力。但当诺亚——一个智力残疾的人，也对常春藤有感情的人，发现他们俩相爱时，诺亚攻击了卢修斯。如果勇敢的常春藤（盲人）不冲破边界，寻求帮助拯救卢修斯，他就会死。

title: Xiao shi de ai ren (2016)
genre: 剧情 悬疑 爱情
cast: Leon Lai , Luodan Wang , Wayne J.J. Lim , Sandrine Pinna , Sau Shek , Emil Ho , Patrick J Molloy , Sunny Sun , Elten Ting , Chuan Wang , Meng-Lin Yang , Crystal Yen
summary: Kaifeng wakes up with a terrible hangover. His heart aches for his lost wife, Qiujie, as memories of the accident rush back to him.It was meant to be a romantic climbing holiday. Both passionate climbers, they decided to summit a mountain in the Himalayas to celebrate their anniversary. But an avalanche dooms him to a lifetime of regret. Qiujie, the love of his life, mother of his son, is gone forever. In despair, Kaifeng turns to a spirit medium for advice on how to bring her back. And to his shock and joy, Qiujie really does come home. But she remembers almost nothing, including their son, and has no memory of the fatal accident. "Only those who love Qiujie will be able to see her spirit. You must never let her know that she's a spirit or she will disappear forever", says the medium. Kaifeng knows that she will not be able to stay forever. He can only try to keep the secret as long as possible with his son. Without letting her know, they try to keep her indoors and away from others while blissfully reliving the wonderful times they had before the accident. Soon the Himalayan climbing accident is uncovered and a body found. The police begin their investigation. At the same time, Qiujie discovers at a party the devastating truth that no one there can see her. She realizes that she is a spirit that must soon part with her husband and their son. She completely falls apart. Using the short time remaining to her, she works to leave a fitting legacy of memories for the future of her family.　　  开封醒来时宿醉难忍。当他回忆起那次事故时，他为失去的妻子秋洁感到心痛。这原本是一个浪漫的登山假期。两人都是热情的登山者，他们决定登上喜马拉雅山脉的一座山峰，庆祝他们的周年纪念日。但雪崩注定了他一生的遗憾。邱杰，他一生的挚爱，他儿子的母亲，已经永远离开了。绝望中，开封求助于一种精神媒介，寻求如何将她带回来的建议。令他震惊和高兴的是，邱杰真的回来了。但她几乎什么都不记得了，包括他们的儿子，也不记得那次致命的事故。媒体说：“只有那些爱秋洁的人才能看到她的灵魂。你千万不要让她知道她是一个灵魂，否则她会永远消失。”。开封知道她不可能永远留在这里。他只能尽量和儿子一起保守秘密。在不让她知道的情况下，他们试图让她呆在家里，远离他人，同时愉快地重温事故前的美好时光。很快，喜马拉雅登山事故被揭露，并发现了一具尸体。警方开始调查。与此同时，秋洁在一次聚会上发现了一个毁灭性的事实：那里没有人能看到她。她意识到自己是一个必须很快与丈夫和儿子分手的灵魂。她完全崩溃了。利用剩下的短暂时间，她努力为家人的未来留下合适的记忆遗产。

summary: Sharon Da Silva wakes up every night screaming about "Silent Hill". title: Xiao shi de ai ren (2016)
genre: 剧情 悬疑 爱情
cast: Leon Lai , Luodan Wang , Wayne J.J. Lim , Sandrine Pinna , Sau Shek , Emil Ho , Patrick J Molloy , Sunny Sun , Elten Ting , Chuan Wang , Meng-Lin Yang , Crystal Yen
summary: Kaifeng wakes up with a terrible hangover. His heart aches for his lost wife, Qiujie, as memories of the accident rush back to him.It was meant to be a romantic climbing holiday. Both passionate climbers, they decided to summit a mountain in the Himalayas to celebrate their anniversary. But an avalanche dooms him to a lifetime of regret. Qiujie, the love of his life, mother of his son, is gone forever. In despair, Kaifeng turns to a spirit medium for advice on how to bring her back. And to his shock and joy, Qiujie really does come home. But she remembers almost nothing, including their son, and has no memory of the fatal accident. "Only those who love Qiujie will be able to see her spirit. You must never let her know that she's a spirit or she will disappear forever", says the medium. Kaifeng knows that she will not be able to stay forever. He can only try to keep the secret as long as possible with his son. Without letting her know, they try to keep her indoors and away from others while blissfully reliving the wonderful times they had before the accident. Soon the Himalayan climbing accident is uncovered and a body found. The police begin their investigation. At the same time, Qiujie discovers at a party the devastating truth that no one there can see her. She realizes that she is a spirit that must soon part with her husband and their son. She completely falls apart. Using the short time remaining to her, she works to leave a fitting legacy of memories for the future of her family.　　  开封醒来时宿醉难忍。当他回忆起那次事故时，他为失去的妻子秋洁感到心痛。这原本是一个浪漫的登山假期。两人都是热情的登山者，他们决定登上喜马拉雅山脉的一座山峰，庆祝他们的周年纪念日。但雪崩注定了他一生的遗憾。邱杰，他一生的挚爱，他儿子的母亲，已经永远离开了。绝望中，开封求助于一种精神媒介，寻求如何将她带回来的建议。令他震惊和高兴的是，邱杰真的回来了。但她几乎什么都不记得了，包括他们的儿子，也不记得那次致命的事故。媒体说：“只有那些爱秋洁的人才能看到她的灵魂。你千万不要让她知道她是一个灵魂，否则她会永远消失。”。开封知道她不可能永远留在这里。他只能尽量和儿子一起保守秘密。在不让她知道的情况下，他们试图让她呆在家里，远离他人，同时愉快地重温事故前的美好时光。很快，喜马拉雅登山事故被揭露，并发现了一具尸体。警方开始调查。与此同时，秋洁在一次聚会上发现了一个毁灭性的事实：那里没有人能看到她。她意识到自己是一个必须很快与丈夫和儿子分手的灵魂。她完全崩溃了。利用剩下的短暂时间，她努力为家人的未来留下合适的记忆遗产。

summary: From acclaimed filmmaker Zhang Meng (Piano in a Factory), the Chinese remake of Giuseppe Tornatore's (Cinema Paradiso) emotionally stirring film follows a widower's visits to his four adult children who lead distinctly different lives in four Chinese cities.It takes an intimate look at the struggling young generation in a nation transitioning from a collective past to a materialist present.　　  由著名电影制作人张萌（《工厂里的钢琴》）改编的朱塞佩·托纳托雷（Giuseppe Tornatore）动人心弦的电影《天堂电影院》（Cinema Paradiso）在中国翻拍，讲述了一位鳏夫探访他在中国四个城市过着截然不同生活的四个成年子女的故事。它深入观察了一个从集体过去过渡到唯物主义现在的国家中挣扎的年轻一代。

title: Day of the Woman (1978)
genre: 恐怖 惊悚
cast: Camille Keaton , Eron Tabor , Richard Pace , Anthony Nichols , Gunter Kleemann , Alexis Magnotti , Tammy Zarchi , Terry Zarchi , Traci Ferrante , William Tasgal , Isaac Agami , Ronit Haviv
summary: Oozing with confidence and the air of a big-city girl, the talented short-story author, Jennifer Hills, arrives in verdant Kent, Connecticut, to take a break from the hustle and bustle of New York City, and write her first novel. But, there, holed up in her secluded riverside cabin, Jennifer is utterly unaware that she has already caught the eye of violent Johnny and his misogynistic jackals, who are hell-bent on having their way with the unsuspecting visitor. And before long, poor Jennifer is sexually assaulted over and over again and left for dead. But, Jennifer is a hard nut to crack, and her fierce will to survive will pave the way for a relentless mission of vengeance. Now, no one is safe. Who can stop Jennifer from tasting the ambrosial nectar of revenge?　　  才华横溢的短篇小说作家詹妮弗·希尔斯（Jennifer Hills）满怀自信和大城市女孩的气质，来到康涅狄格州葱郁的肯特（Kent），从纽约市的喧嚣中解脱出来，写下了她的第一部小说。但是，就在那里，躲在她僻静的河边小屋里，詹妮弗完全没有意识到她已经引起了暴力的约翰尼和他厌恶女性的豺狼的注意，他们对这位毫无戒心的来访者不屑一顾。不久，可怜的詹妮弗遭到了一次又一次的性侵，最后被遗弃。但是，珍妮弗是一个难以攻克的难题，她强烈的求生意志将为无情的复仇任务铺平道路。现在，没有人是安全的。谁能阻止珍妮弗尝到复仇的甘露？

summary: A young Kung Fu student (Shih Szu) seeks a reclusive teacher so that she may learn to defeat the evil Black Demon. cast: Pei-Pei Cheng , Lo Lieh , Szu Shih , Hsieh Wang , Mien Fang , Hsiung Chao , Yuan Chuan , Tien-Hsi Tang , Hsiao-Chung Li , Han Lo , Chia-Hsi Hu , Hua Hsiao , Shao-Hung Chan , Ming Chin , Chia-Chung Chou , Chiang Chou , Chin Chun , Ling Han
summary: A young Kung Fu student (Shih Szu) seeks a reclusive teacher so that she may learn to defeat the evil Black Demon. She doesn't realize that the servant woman she befriends (Cheng Pei-Pei) is actually the kung fu master she seeks. After Black Demons henchmen attack, the master reveals herself and eventually takes on the student to train her so that they may both defeat the villian. A love triangle complicates things when another student (Lo Lieh) asks for training as well.　　  一位年轻的功夫学生（Shih Szu）寻找一位隐居的老师，以便她可以学习击败邪恶的黑魔王。她没有意识到，她结识的女佣人（程佩佩饰）实际上就是她所寻找的功夫大师。在黑魔王的追随者攻击后，主人暴露了自己，并最终让学生训练她，这样他们就可以打败这个恶棍。当另一名学生（Lo Lieh）也要求培训时，三角恋会使事情复杂化。

title: The Last Letter from Your Lover (2021)
genre: 剧情 爱情
cast: Shailene Woodley , Joe Alwyn , Wendy Nottingham , Felicity Jones , Jacob Fortune-Lloyd , Ncuti Gatwa , Emma Appleton , Jessica D'Arcy , Ann Ogbomo , Nabhaan Rizwan , Alice Orr-Ewing , Zoe Boyle , Christian Brassington , Lee Knight , Rachel Atkins , Jasmine Hyde , Callum Turner , Atheena Frizzell
summary: A pair of interwoven stories set in the present and past follows Ellie Haworth, an ambitious journalist who discovers a trove of secret love letters from 1965 and becomes determined to solve the mystery of the forbidden affair at their center. As she uncovers the story behind Jennifer Stirling, the wife of a wealthy industrialist, and Anthony O'Hare, the financial journalist assigned to cover him, Ellie's own love story unfolds with the assistance of an earnest, endearing archivist who helps her track down more letters.　　  一对交织在现在和过去的故事讲述了一位雄心勃勃的记者Ellie Haworth的故事，她发现了1965年的一批秘密情书，并决心在其中心破解这桩被禁止的婚外情的秘密。当她揭开一位富有实业家的妻子詹妮弗·斯特林（Jennifer Stirling）和金融记者安东尼·奥黑尔（Anthony O'Hare）背后的故事时，埃莉自己的爱情故事在一位真诚可爱的档案管理员的帮助下展开，这位档案管理员帮她找到了更多的信件。

title: The Last Picture Show (1971)
genre: 剧情 爱情
cast: Timothy Bottoms , Jeff Bridges , Cybill Shepherd , Ben Johnson , Cloris Leachman , Ellen Burstyn , Eileen Brennan , Clu Gulager , Sam Bottoms , Sharon Ullrick , Randy Quaid , Joe Heathcock , Bill Thurman , Barc Doyle , Jessie Lee Fulton , Gary Brockette , Helena Humann , Loyd Catlett
summary: In tiny Anarene, Texas, in the lull between World War Two and the Korean Conflict, Sonny and Duane are best friends. Enduring that awkward period of life between boyhood and manhood, the two pass their time the best way they know how -- with the movie house, football, and girls. Jacy is Duane's steady, wanted by every boy in school, and she knows it. Her daddy is rich and her mom is good looking and loose. It's the general consensus that whoever wins Jacy's heart will be set for life. But Anarene is dying a quiet death as folks head for the big cities to make their livings and raise their kids. The boys are torn between a future somewhere out there beyond the borders of town or making do with their inheritance of a run-down pool hall and a decrepit movie house -- the legacy of their friend and mentor, Sam the Lion. As high school graduation approaches, they learn some difficult lessons about love, loneliness, and jealousy. Then folks stop attending the second-run features at the movie house and the time comes for the last picture show. With the closure of the movie house, the boys feel that a stage of their lives is closing. They stand uneasily on the threshold of the rest of their lives. (The movie was adapted from the novel by Larry McMurtry).　　  在得克萨斯州的阿纳雷内，在二战和朝鲜冲突之间的平静时期，桑尼和杜安是最好的朋友。在经历了童年和成年之间的尴尬时期后，两人以他们所知道的最佳方式度过了时光——与电影院、足球和女孩一起度过。杰西是杜安的忠实伴侣，是学校里每个男孩都想要的人，她知道这一点。她的爸爸很富有，她的妈妈长得很好看，很放荡。人们普遍认为，无论谁赢得杰西的心，都将终身受用。但随着人们前往大城市谋生和抚养孩子，阿纳雷内正在悄无声息地死去。孩子们在城市边界之外的未来和他们继承的一个破旧的游泳馆和一个破败的电影院之间左右为难，这是他们的朋友和导师，狮子山姆的遗产。随着高中毕业的临近，他们学到了一些关于爱情、孤独和嫉妒的艰难教训。然后人们就不再去电影院看第二轮特写了，是时候看最后一场电影了。随着电影院的关闭，男孩们感到他们生活的一个阶段即将结束。他们不安地站在余生的门槛上。（这部电影改编自拉里·麦克默里的小说）。

summary: A high school student named Jake tries to make his girlfriend Emily watch a cursed tape. But then Jake finds out that Emily covered her eyes and didn't watch the tape, and then Jake is killed by Samara Morgan (from the first The Ring movie). Rachel Keller learns of Jake's death and finds his twisted body in the back of an ambulance. Rachel then realizes she once again has to save her son Aidan from Samara the evil ghost child.　　  一个名叫杰克的高中生试图让他的女朋友艾米丽看一盘被诅咒的磁带。但后来杰克发现艾米丽遮住了眼睛，没有看录像，于是杰克被萨马拉·摩根（Samara Morgan）杀死了（摘自第一部《魔戒》电影）。雷切尔·凯勒得知杰克的死讯后，在救护车后面发现了他扭曲的尸体。瑞秋随后意识到，她必须再次从邪恶的鬼孩子萨马拉手中救出她的儿子艾丹。
