title: On Wings of Eagles (2016)
genre: 传记 剧情 历史
cast: Joseph Fiennes , Jesse Kove , Bruce Locke , Shawn Dou , Elizabeth Arends , Zach Ireland , Richard Sanderson , Kuo-Chu Chang , Simon Twu , Augusta Xu-Holland , Darren Grosvenor , Asano Nagahide , Shigeo Kobayashi , Patrice Poujol , Xiaoqian Liu , Elizabeth Yufei Gabriel , Wai-Lam Wong , Yongqing Liu
summary: Eric Liddell may have won gold for the United Kingdom and possessed a lilting Highland brogue, but he was born in China and lived more than half his life there evangelizing and teaching. title: The Last Picture Show (1971)
genre: 剧情 爱情
cast: Timothy Bottoms , Jeff Bridges , Cybill Shepherd , Ben Johnson , Cloris Leachman , Ellen Burstyn , Eileen Brennan , Clu Gulager , Sam Bottoms , Sharon Ullrick , Randy Quaid , Joe Heathcock , Bill Thurman , Barc Doyle , Jessie Lee Fulton , Gary Brockette , Helena Humann , Loyd Catlett
summary: In tiny Anarene, Texas, in the lull between World War Two and the Korean Conflict, Sonny and Duane are best friends. Enduring that awkward period of life between boyhood and manhood, the two pass their time the best way they know how -- with the movie house, football, and girls. Jacy is Duane's steady, wanted by every boy in school, and she knows it. Her daddy is rich and her mom is good looking and loose. It's the general consensus that whoever wins Jacy's heart will be set for life. But Anarene is dying a quiet death as folks head for the big cities to make their livings and raise their kids. The boys are torn between a future somewhere out there beyond the borders of town or making do with their inheritance of a run-down pool hall and a decrepit movie house -- the legacy of their friend and mentor, Sam the Lion. As high school graduation approaches, they learn some difficult lessons about love, loneliness, and jealousy. Then folks stop attending the second-run features at the movie house and the time comes for the last picture show. With the closure of the movie house, the boys feel that a stage of their lives is closing. They stand uneasily on the threshold of the rest of their lives. (The movie was adapted from the novel by Larry McMurtry).　　  在得克萨斯州的阿纳雷内，在二战和朝鲜冲突之间的平静时期，桑尼和杜安是最好的朋友。在经历了童年和成年之间的尴尬时期后，两人以他们所知道的最佳方式度过了时光——与电影院、足球和女孩一起度过。杰西是杜安的忠实伴侣，是学校里每个男孩都想要的人，她知道这一点。她的爸爸很富有，她的妈妈长得很好看，很放荡。人们普遍认为，无论谁赢得杰西的心，都将终身受用。但随着人们前往大城市谋生和抚养孩子，阿纳雷内正在悄无声息地死去。孩子们在城市边界之外的未来和他们继承的一个破旧的游泳馆和一个破败的电影院之间左右为难，这是他们的朋友和导师，狮子山姆的遗产。随着高中毕业的临近，他们学到了一些关于爱情、孤独和嫉妒的艰难教训。然后人们就不再去电影院看第二轮特写了，是时候看最后一场电影了。随着电影院的关闭，男孩们感到他们生活的一个阶段即将结束。他们不安地站在余生的门槛上。（这部电影改编自拉里·麦克默里的小说）。

summary: This movie tells the true story of Alan Bennett's (Alex Jennings') strained friendship with Miss Mary Shepherd (Dame Maggie Smith), an eccentric homeless woman who Bennett befriended in the 1970s before allowing her temporarily to park her Bedford van in the driveway of his Camden house. She stayed there for fifteen years. As the story develops, Bennett learns that Miss Shepherd is really Margaret Fairchild (died 1989), a former gifted pupil of pianist Alfred Cortot. She had played Chopin in a promenade concert, tried to become a nun, was committed to an institution by her brother, escaped, had an accident when her van was hit by a motorcyclist for which she believed herself to blame, and thereafter lived in fear of arrest.　　  这部电影讲述了阿兰·贝内特（亚历克斯·詹宁斯饰）与玛丽·谢泼德小姐（玛吉·史密斯爵士饰）紧张友谊的真实故事。玛丽·谢伯德小姐是一位古怪的无家可归的女人，贝内特在20世纪70年代与她结为好友，之后才允许她暂时将贝德福德面包车停在卡姆登家的车道上。她在那里呆了十五年。随着故事的发展，贝内特得知谢泼德小姐真的是玛格丽特·费尔柴尔德（1989年去世），她曾是钢琴家阿尔弗雷德·科尔托的天才学生。她曾在一场长廊音乐会上演奏肖邦的作品，试图成为一名修女，被哥哥送到了一家机构，后来逃跑了，她的货车被一名摩托车手撞了，发生了事故，她认为自己应该为此负责，此后她一直生活在被逮捕的恐惧中。

title: The Lady Vanishes (1938)
genre: 犯罪 剧情 悬疑
cast: Margaret Lockwood , Michael Redgrave , Paul Lukas , May Whitty , Cecil Parker , Linden Travers , Naunton Wayne , Basil Radford , Mary Clare , Emile Boreo , Googie Withers , Sally Stewart , Philip Leaver , Selma Vaz Dias , Catherine Lacey , Josephine Wilson , Charles Oliver , Kathleen Tremaine
summary: Passengers on a scheduled train out of the mountainous European country of Mandrika are delayed by a day due to an avalanche, and thus get up close and personal with each other out of necessity in the only and what becomes an overcrowded inn in the area. Once the train departs, the one person who it is uncertain is on the train is a middle aged English governess named Miss Froy (Dame May Whitty). Iris Henderson (Margaret Lockwood), who was vacationing in Mandrika with girlfriends before heading back to England to get married, is certain that Miss Froy was on the train as they were in the same compartment and they had tea together in the dining car, but all those people who can corroborate her story don't seem to want to do so. Iris' thoughts are easily dismissed as a possible concussion as Iris was hit over the head just before boarding the train. Iris will take anyone's help in finding Miss Froy, even that of an Englishman named Gilbert (Sir Michael Redgrave), a musicologist with whom she had a not so pleasant encounter at the inn the evening before. As Iris and Gilbert go on their quest throughout the train, they believe there is a conspiracy amongst many of the passengers against the validity of there being a Miss Froy. But if there is a conspiracy, Iris and Gilbert still have to find Miss Froy and find out why anyone would want to kidnap a middle aged English governess.　　  从欧洲多山国家曼德里卡出发的定期火车上的乘客因雪崩而延误了一天，因此，在该地区唯一一家人满为患的客栈里，出于必要，他们彼此亲密接触。火车一开，车上就有一位不确定的中年英国家庭教师，名叫弗罗伊小姐（梅·惠蒂夫人）。艾丽斯·亨德森（玛格丽特·洛克伍德饰）在回英国结婚前与女友在曼德里卡度假，她确信弗罗伊小姐当时在火车上，就像他们在同一车厢里一样，他们一起在餐车里喝茶，但所有能证实她的故事的人似乎都不想这样做。艾瑞斯的想法很容易被认为是一种可能的脑震荡，因为艾瑞斯在上车前头部被击中。艾丽斯会在任何人的帮助下找到弗罗伊小姐，甚至是一位名叫吉尔伯特（迈克尔·雷德格雷夫爵士）的英国人，他是一位音乐学家，前一天晚上她在酒店遇到了一位不太愉快的人。当艾丽斯和吉尔伯特在火车上四处寻找时，他们认为许多乘客之间存在着一个阴谋，反对弗洛伊小姐的存在。但如果有阴谋，艾丽斯和吉尔伯特仍然必须找到弗罗伊小姐，并找出为什么有人想绑架一位中年英国家庭教师。

summary: Robert Redford stars in this action drama as General Irwin, a respected three-star tactician whose career ends in disgrace when he's court-martialed and sent to The Castle, a maximum security military prison. Irwin rallies his fellow convicts into a rag-tag army and leads them in a revolt against Winter, an action that the warden is ready to repel by violent means.　　  罗伯特·雷德福德（Robert Redford）在这部动作片中饰演欧文将军（General Irwin），他是一位受人尊敬的三星级战术大师，在法庭上大放异彩并被送往最高安全级别的军事监狱城堡（The Castle）后，他的职业生涯以耻辱告终。欧文很快与该设施的独裁典狱长温特上校（詹姆斯·甘多尔菲尼饰）发生冲突，温特上校用铁拳指挥，甚至在他认为必要时杀害囚犯。欧文将他的囚犯同伴召集成一支破烂军队，带领他们反抗温特，监狱长准备用暴力手段予以击退。

cast: Robert Redford , James Gandolfini , Mark Ruffalo , Steve Burton , Delroy Lindo , Paul Calderon , Sam Ball , Jeremy Childs , Clifton Collins Jr. , George W. Scott , Brian Goodman , Michael Irby , Frank Military , Maurice Bullard , Nick Kokich , David Alford , Dean Hall , Peg Allen
summary: Robert Redford stars in this action drama as General Irwin, a respected three-star tactician whose career ends in disgrace when he's court-martialed and sent to The Castle, a maximum security military prison. Irwin quickly butts heads with the facility's autocratic warden, Colonel Winter (James Gandolfini), who runs his command with an iron fist, even killing prisoners when he deems it necessary. Irwin rallies his fellow convicts into a rag-tag army and leads them in a revolt against Winter, an action that the warden is ready to repel by violent means.　　  罗伯特·雷德福德（Robert Redford）在这部动作片中饰演欧文将军（General Irwin），他是一位受人尊敬的三星级战术大师，在法庭上大放异彩并被送往最高安全级别的军事监狱城堡（The Castle）后，他的职业生涯以耻辱告终。欧文很快与该设施的独裁典狱长温特上校（詹姆斯·甘多尔菲尼饰）发生冲突，温特上校用铁拳指挥，甚至在他认为必要时杀害囚犯。欧文将他的囚犯同伴召集成一支破烂军队，带领他们反抗温特，监狱长准备用暴力手段予以击退。

title: The Last Detail (1973)
genre: 喜剧 剧情
cast: Jack Nicholson , Randy Quaid , Otis Young , Clifton James , Carol Kane , Michael Moriarty , Luana Anders , Kathleen Miller , Nancy Allen , Gerry Salsberg , Don McGovern , Patricia Hamilton , Michael Chapman , Jim Henshaw , Derek McGrath , Gilda Radner , Jim Horn , John Castellano
summary: Two bawdy, tough looking navy lifers - "Bad-Ass" Buddusky, and "Mule" Mulhall - are commissioned to escort a young pilferer named Meadows to the brig in Portsmouth. Meadows is not much of a thief. Indeed, in his late teens, he is not much of a man at all. His great crime was to try to steal forty dollars from the admiral's wife's pet charity. For this, he's been sentenced to eight years behind bars. At first, Buddusky and Mulhall view the journey as a paid vacation, but their holiday spirits are quickly depressed by the prisoner, who looks prepared to break into tears at any moment. And he has the lowest self-image imaginable. Buddusky gets it into his head to give Meadows a good time and teach him a bit about getting on in the world. Lesson one

summary: Based on the true story of France's last trial by combat in the Middle Ages. Knight Jean de Carrouges challenges his former friend Jacques Le Gris to a duel after Jean's wife Marguerite accuses Le Gris of rape. Told in multiple "Rashomon-style" points of view.　　  基于中世纪法国最后一次战斗的真实故事。在让的妻子玛格丽特指控勒格里斯强奸后，骑士让·德·卡鲁日向他的前朋友雅克·勒格里斯挑战决斗。以多种“罗生门式”观点讲述。

genre: 剧情 历史 惊悚
cast: Matt Damon , Adam Driver , Jodie Comer , Harriet Walter , Ben Affleck , Alex Lawther , Marton Csokas , William Houston , Oliver Cotton , Aurélien Lorgnier , Nathaniel Parker , Tallulah Haddon , Bryony Hannah , Thomas Silberstein , Adam Goodwin , Ian Pirie , Daniel Horn , Michael McElhatton
summary: Based on the true story of France's last trial by combat in the Middle Ages. Knight Jean de Carrouges challenges his former friend Jacques Le Gris to a duel after Jean's wife Marguerite accuses Le Gris of rape. Told in multiple "Rashomon-style" points of view.　　  基于中世纪法国最后一次战斗的真实故事。在让的妻子玛格丽特指控勒格里斯强奸后，骑士让·德·卡鲁日向他的前朋友雅克·勒格里斯挑战决斗。以多种“罗生门式”观点讲述。

title: The Last Emperor (1987)
genre: 传记 剧情 历史
cast: John Lone , Joan Chen , Peter O'Toole , Ruocheng Ying , Victor Wong , Dennis Dun , Ryuichi Sakamoto , Maggie Han , Ric Young , Vivian Wu , Cary-Hiroyuki Tagawa , Jade Go , Fumihiko Ikeda , Richard Vuu , Tsou Tijger , Tao Wu , Guang Fan , Henry Kyi
summary: This sweeping account of the life of Pu-Yi, the last emperor of China, follows the leader's tumultuous reign. After being captured by the Red Army as a war criminal in 1950, Pu-Yi recalls his childhood from prison. He remembers his lavish youth in the Forbidden City, where he was afforded every luxury but unfortunately sheltered from the outside world and complex political situation surrounding him. As revolution sweeps through China, the world Pu-Yi knew is dramatically upended.　　  这篇关于中国末代皇帝溥仪生平的全面记述，紧随着这位领导人动荡的统治。1950年作为战犯被红军俘虏后，溥仪回忆起自己在狱中的童年。他还记得自己在紫禁城的奢侈少年时代，在那里，他得到了一切奢侈品，但不幸的是，他受到了外界和复杂政治局势的庇护。随着革命席卷中国，溥仪所认识的世界被彻底颠覆。

title: The Last Full Measure (2019)
genre: 剧情 战争
cast: Sebastian Stan , Alison Sudol , Asher Miles Fallica , LisaGay Hamilton , Bradley Whitford , William Hurt , Linus Roache , Jeremy Irvine , Christopher Plummer , Diane Ladd , Samuel L. Jackson , Amy Madigan , Peter Fonda , Ed Harris , John Savage , Ser'Darius Blain , Julian Adams , James Jagger
summary: In 1999 an up-and-coming political staffer at the Department of Defence, Scott Huffman, is given the job of investigating a request to upgrade an award to the Medal of Honour. After conspicuous acts of gallantry Airman William H Pitsenbarger was killed in Vietnam in 1966. He was recommended for the MoH but his award was downgraded to the Air Force Cross. For over 30 years his comrades and family have been lobbying for him to receive the medal. Huffman cares more about his own career than this case but the more he looks into it, the more convinced he is that Pitsenbarger deserves the MoH and should have received it in 1966. Why didn't he then?　　  1999年，国防部一位崭露头角的政治工作人员斯科特·霍夫曼（Scott Huffman）受命调查一项将奖项升级为荣誉勋章的请求。1966年，威廉·H·皮特森巴格（William H Pitsenbarger）空军飞行员在英勇无畏的行为后在越南被杀。他被推荐加入卫生部，但他的奖项被降级为空军十字勋章。30多年来，他的同志和家人一直在游说他获得奖牌。哈夫曼更关心自己的职业生涯，而不是这件事，但他越是深入调查，就越是确信皮特森巴格应该得到卫生部的任命，而且应该在1966年获得。那他为什么没有呢？

title: The Last Full Measure (2019)
genre: 剧情 战争
cast: Sebastian Stan , Alison Sudol , Asher Miles Fallica , LisaGay Hamilton , Bradley Whitford , William Hurt , Linus Roache , Jeremy Irvine , Christopher Plummer , Diane Ladd , Samuel L. Jackson , Amy Madigan , Peter Fonda , Ed Harris , John Savage , Ser'Darius Blain , Julian Adams , James Jagger
summary: In 1999 an up-and-coming political staffer at the Department of Defence, Scott Huffman, is given the job of investigating a request to upgrade an award to the Medal of Honour. After conspicuous acts of gallantry Airman William H Pitsenbarger was killed in Vietnam in 1966. He was recommended for the MoH but his award was downgraded to the Air Force Cross. For over 30 years his comrades and family have been lobbying for him to receive the medal. Huffman cares more about his own career than this case but the more he looks into it, the more convinced he is that Pitsenbarger deserves the MoH and should have received it in 1966. Why didn't he then?　　  1999年，国防部一位崭露头角的政治工作人员斯科特·霍夫曼（Scott Huffman）受命调查一项将奖项升级为荣誉勋章的请求。1966年，威廉·H·皮特森巴格（William H Pitsenbarger）空军飞行员在英勇无畏的行为后在越南被杀。他被推荐加入卫生部，但他的奖项被降级为空军十字勋章。30多年来，他的同志和家人一直在游说他获得奖牌。哈夫曼更关心自己的职业生涯，而不是这件事，但他越是深入调查，就越是确信皮特森巴格应该得到卫生部的任命，而且应该在1966年获得。那他为什么没有呢？

title: The Karate Kid (2010)
genre: 动作 剧情 家庭
cast: Jackie Chan , Jaden Smith , Taraji P. Henson , Wenwen Han , Rongguang Yu , Zhensu Wu , Zhiheng Wang , Zhenwei Wang , Jared Minns , Shijia Lü , Yi Zhao , Bo Zhang , Luke Carberry , Cameron Hillman , Ghye Samuel Brown , Rocky Shi , Ji Wang , Harry Van Gorkum
summary: 12-year-old Dre Parker has moved to China, and finds himself like a fish out of water. He befriends a fellow classmate, Mei Ying, only to make a rival, Cheng, who starts to bully and attack Dre. Soon, Mr Han, the maintenance man of Dre's apartment, fends off Cheng and his friends when they are attacking Dre and signs Dre up to fight in the Kung Fu tournament in return for the bullies laying off of Dre. Dre realizes Mr. Han is much more than a maintenance man, when he's revealed as a master of Kung Fu and Dre soon learns that Kung Fu is about self defense and peace, instead of violence and bloodshed.　　  12岁的德雷·帕克（Dre Parker）搬到了中国，发现自己就像一条离开了水的鱼。他和同学梅英交上了朋友，却结成了对手程，程开始欺负和攻击德雷。很快，当程和他的朋友攻击德雷时，德雷公寓的维修工韩先生挡住了他们，并签约德雷参加武术锦标赛，以换取德雷被恶霸解雇。德雷意识到韩先生不仅仅是一个维修工，当他被透露为功夫大师时，德雷很快就明白了功夫是关于自卫与和平，而不是暴力与流血。

title: The Kid (1921)
genre: 喜剧 剧情 家庭
cast: Charles Chaplin , Edna Purviance , Jackie Coogan , Carl Miller , Albert Austin , Beulah Bains , Nellie Bly Baker , Henry Bergman , Edward Biby , B.F. Blinn , Kitty Bradbury , Frank Campeau , Bliss Chevalier , Frances Cochran , Elsie Codd , Jack Coogan Sr. , Estelle Cook , Lillian Crane
summary: A woman decides to abandon her baby in the backseat of an automobile with a handwritten note attached, beseeching the finder to care for and love the child. summary: After just being released from a five-year stint in prison, Johnny Clay has assembled a five-man team, including two insiders, to carry out what he estimates will be a $2 million heist at Lansdowne Racetrack, the take to be split five ways, minus expenses. Besides Johnny, none of the men truly are criminals in the typical sense. In addition to the other four team members, Johnny has hired two men outside of the team to carry out specific functions for a flat fee; the other four will not meet the two men for hire or know who they are, while the two men for hire will not be told of the bigger picture of the heist. None involved are to tell anyone, even their loved ones, about the job. Each of the five have a specific reason for wanting his share of the money

title: The Killing (1956)
genre: 犯罪 剧情 黑色电影
cast: Sterling Hayden , Coleen Gray , Vince Edwards , Jay C. Flippen , Ted de Corsia , Marie Windsor , Elisha Cook Jr. , Joe Sawyer , James Edwards , Timothy Carey , Kola Kwariani , Jay Adler , Tito Vuolo , Dorothy Adams , Herbert Ellis , James Griffith , Cecil Elliott , Joe Turkel
summary: After just being released from a five-year stint in prison, Johnny Clay has assembled a five-man team, including two insiders, to carry out what he estimates will be a $2 million heist at Lansdowne Racetrack, the take to be split five ways, minus expenses. Besides Johnny, none of the men truly are criminals in the typical sense. In addition to the other four team members, Johnny has hired two men outside of the team to carry out specific functions for a flat fee; the other four will not meet the two men for hire or know who they are, while the two men for hire will not be told of the bigger picture of the heist. None involved are to tell anyone, even their loved ones, about the job. Each of the five have a specific reason for wanting his share of the money

title: The Killing Fields (1984)
genre: 传记 剧情 历史
cast: Sam Waterston , Haing S. Ngor , John Malkovich , Julian Sands , Craig T. Nelson , Spalding Gray , Bill Paterson , Athol Fugard , Graham Kennedy , Katherine Krapum Chey , Oliver Pierpaoli , Edward Entero Chey , Tom Bird , Monirak Sisowath , Lambool Dtangpaibool , Ira Wheeler , David Henry , Patrick Malahide
summary: Sydney Schanberg is a New York Times journalist covering the civil war in Cambodia. Together with the local journalist Dith Pran, they cover some of the tragedy and madness of the war. When the American forces leave, Dith Pran sends his family with them, but stays behind himself to help Schanberg cover the event. As an American, Schanberg won't have any trouble leaving the country, but the situation is different for Pran; he's a local, and the Khmer Rouge are moving in.　　  西德尼·桑伯格是《纽约时报》记者，报道柬埔寨内战。他们与当地记者迪思·普兰一起报道了战争的一些悲剧和疯狂。美国军队离开后，迪思·普兰（Dith Pran）派遣家人与他们一同前往，但留下来帮助申伯格（Schanberg）报道这一事件。作为一名美国人，Schanberg离开美国不会有任何困难，但Pran的情况不同；他是当地人，红色高棉正在搬进来。

title: The Killing of a Chinese Bookie (1976)
genre: 犯罪 剧情 惊悚
cast: Ben Gazzara , Timothy Carey , Seymour Cassel , Robert Phillips , Morgan Woodward , John Kullers , Al Ruban , Azizi Johari , Virginia Carrington , Meade Roberts , Alice Friedland , Donna Gordon , Haji , Carol Warren , Kathalina Veniero , Yvette Morris , Jack Ackerman , David Rowlands
summary: Cosmo Vitelli owns the Crazy Horse West, a strip joint in Los Angeles. He's laconic, vet, and a gambler. When we meet him, he's making his last payment on a gambling debt, after which, he promptly loses $23,000 playing poker. The guys he owes this time aren't so friendly, pressuring him for immediate payment. When he's not able to do so, they suggest he kill a Chinese bookie to wipe away his debt. Vitelli and the film move back and forth between the double-crossing, murderous insincerity of the gamblers and the friendships, sweetness, and even love among Vitelli, the dancers, a dancer's mother, and the club's singer, Mr. Sophistication.　　  Cosmo Vitelli拥有洛杉矶的一家脱衣舞厅Crazy Horse West。他口齿不清，是个兽医，也是个赌徒。当我们见到他时，他正在支付最后一笔赌债，之后，他在玩扑克时立即损失了23000美元。这次欠他的人不太友好，迫使他立即付款。当他无法做到这一点时，他们建议他杀了一家中国博彩公司来还清债务。维泰利和这部电影在赌徒的双重交叉、凶残的虚伪与维泰利、舞者、舞者的母亲和俱乐部的歌手索菲斯蒂安之间的友谊、甜蜜甚至爱情之间来回穿梭。

title: The Killing of a Sacred Deer (2017)
genre: 剧情 恐怖 悬疑
cast: Barry G. Bernson , Herb Caillouet , Bill Camp , Raffey Cassidy , Denise Dal Vera , Colin Farrell , Barry Keoghan , Nicole Kidman , Drew Logan , Alicia Silverstone , Sunny Suljic , Michael Trester , Ming Wang , Dylan Keith Adams , Mike Ancas , Michael Lee Bailey , Denise Barone , Lea Hutton Beasmore
summary: After the untimely death of 16-year-old Martin's father on the operating table, little by little, a deep and empathetic bond begins to form between him and the respected cardiothoracic surgeon, Dr Steven Murphy. At first, expensive gifts and then an invitation for dinner will soon earn the orphaned teenager the approval of Dr Steven's perfect family, even though right from the start, a vague, yet unnerving feeling overshadows Martin's honest intent. And then, unexpectedly, the idyllic family is smote by a fierce and pitiless punishment, while at the same time, everything will start falling apart as the innocents have to suffer. In the end, as the sins of one burden the entire family, only an unimaginable and unendurable decision that demands a pure sacrifice can purge the soul. summary: Rupert Pupkin is obsessed with becoming a comedy great. He does not give up, however, but persists in stalking Jerry until he gets what he wants. Eventually he must team up with his psychotic Langford-obsessed friend Masha to kidnap the talk show host in hopes of finally getting to perform his stand-up routine.　　  鲁珀特·普金痴迷于成为喜剧大师。然而，当他面对他的偶像脱口秀主持人杰里·兰福德时，他请求在杰里的脱口秀节目中表演，却只得到了回避。然而，他并没有放弃，而是坚持跟踪杰瑞，直到他得到他想要的。最终，他必须与他痴迷于朗福德的精神病朋友玛莎联手绑架这位脱口秀主持人，以期最终能够表演他的单口秀节目。

summary: WE ARE AS GODS offers a compelling deep dive into the many sides of Stewart Brand - creator of The Whole Earth Catalog, an influential member of Ken Kesey's "The Merry Pranksters," a founder of the modern environmental movement, and today a vocal advocate for bringing back extinct species of animals and plants. Brand's approach to his work and life influenced many, including Steve Jobs, who have gone on to shape our modern world. Now in his 80's, he looks to leave a legacy for the future with his Long Now Foundation and efforts to "enhance biodiversity through the genetic rescue of extinct and endangered species." The man who coined the phrase "we are as gods and might as well get good at it" is now under fire from former allies who believe he's gone too far, but Brand won't be easily deterred from a mission he feels is necessary to save the future of the planet.　　  《我们是上帝》（WE ARE AS GODS）对斯图尔特·布兰德（Stewart Brand）的许多方面进行了令人信服的深入探讨，斯图尔特是《地球目录》（the Whole Earth Catalog）的创作者，肯·凯西（Ken Kesey）的《快乐的恶作剧者》（the Merry Pranksters）的有影响力的成员，现代环境运动的创始人，今天，斯图尔特·布兰德是一。布兰德的工作和生活方式影响了许多人，包括史蒂夫·乔布斯，他塑造了我们的现代世界。现在他已经80多岁了，他希望通过长期基金会和“通过对灭绝和濒危物种的基因拯救来加强生物多样性”的努力，为未来留下一笔遗产。这个创造了“我们就像神一样，也许还不如做得好”这句话的人现在受到了前盟友的抨击，他们认为他做得太过分了，但布兰德不会轻易放弃他认为拯救地球未来所必需的使命。

title: Rain Man (1988)
genre: 剧情
cast: Dustin Hoffman  ,  Tom Cruise  ,  Valeria Golino  ,  Gerald R. Molen  ,  Jack Murdock  ,  Michael D. Roberts  ,  Ralph Seymour  ,  Lucinda Jenney  ,  Bonnie Hunt  ,  Kim Robillard  ,  Beth Grant  ,  Dolan Dougherty  ,  Marshall Dougherty  ,  Patrick Dougherty  ,  John-Michael Dougherty  ,  Peter Dougherty  ,  Andrew Dougherty  ,  Loretta Wendt Jolivette
summary: Charles Sanford "Charlie" Babbit is a self-centered Los Angeles-based automobile dealer/hustler/bookie who is at war with his own life. Charlie, as a young teenager, used his father's 1949 Buick convertible without permission and as a result, he went to jail for two days on account that his father reported it stolen. It is then that Charlie learns that his estranged father died and left him from his last will and testament a huge bed of roses and the car while the remainder will of $3 Million goes into a trust fund to be distributed to someone. Charlie seemed pretty angry by this and decides to look into this matter. It seems as if that "someone" is Raymond, Charlie's unknown brother, an autistic savant who lives in a world of his own, resides at the Walbrook Institute. Charlie then kidnaps Raymond and decides to take him on a lust for life trip to the west coast as a threat to get the $3 Million inheritance. Raymond's acts and nagging, including repeated talks of "Abbott & Costello", "Four minutes till Wapner" and refusal to fly on an airline except Qantas drives Charlie insane... and out of his selfish world into a cross-country trek of pure love and understanding that these two both have.　　  查尔斯·桑福德（Charles Sanford）“查理”·巴比特（Charlie Babbit）是一位以自我为中心的洛杉矶汽车经销商/骗子/赌徒，他与自己的生活格格不入。年轻时，查理未经许可使用父亲的1949年别克敞篷车，结果因父亲报案称其被盗而入狱两天。就在那时，查理得知他疏远的父亲去世了，并在他最后的遗嘱和遗嘱中留下了一张巨大的玫瑰床和一辆汽车，而剩余的300万美元将存入一个信托基金，以分配给某人。查理对此似乎很生气，决定调查此事。这个“人”似乎就是雷蒙德，查理的不为人知的哥哥，一位生活在自己世界里的孤独症学者，住在沃尔布鲁克研究所。随后，查理绑架了雷蒙德，并决定带他去西海岸进行一次性欲之旅，以此作为获得300万美元遗产的威胁。雷蒙德的行为和唠叨，包括反复谈论“Abbott&Costello”、“离Wapner还有四分钟”，以及除了澳洲航空公司（Qantas）之外拒绝乘坐其他航空公司的航班，都让查理精神错乱。。。走出他自私的世界，踏上这两个人所拥有的纯洁爱情和理解的越野之旅。

title: The Iron Lady (2011)
genre: 传记 剧情
cast: Meryl Streep , Jim Broadbent , Richard E. Grant , Susan Brown , Alice da Cunha , Phoebe Waller-Bridge , Iain Glen , Alexandra Roach , Victoria Bewick , Emma Dewhurst , Olivia Colman , Harry Lloyd , Sylvestra Le Touzel , Michael Culkin , Stephanie Jacob , Robert Portal , Richard Dixon , Amanda Root
summary: Elderly and a virtual prisoner in her own home due to her concerned staff and daughter Carol, Margaret Thatcher, Britain's first woman prime minister, looks back on her life as she clears out her late husband Denis's clothes for the Oxfam shop. Denis is seen as being her rock as she first enters parliament and then runs for the leadership of the Conservative Party, culminating in her eventual premiership. Now his ghost joins her to comment on her successes and failures, sometimes to her annoyance, generally to her comfort until ultimately, as the clothes are sent to the charity shop, Denis departs from Margaret's life forever.　　  英国第一位女首相玛格丽特·撒切尔（Margaret Thatcher）是一位年长的女性，由于她的工作人员和女儿卡罗尔（Carol）的担忧，她实际上被囚禁在自己的家中。她在为乐施会商店清理已故丈夫丹尼斯（Denis）的衣服时回顾了自己的生活。丹尼斯（Denis）最初进入议会，然后竞选保守党领导层，最终成为首相，被视为她的摇滚乐手。现在，他的鬼魂和她一起评论她的成功和失败，有时会让她恼火，通常会让她感到安慰，直到最后，当衣服被送到慈善商店时，丹尼斯永远离开了玛格丽特的生活。

title: The Italian Job (1969)

cast: Michael Caine , Noël Coward , Benny Hill , Raf Vallone , Tony Beckley , Rossano Brazzi , Margaret Blye , Irene Handl , John Le Mesurier , Fred Emney , John Clive , Graham Payn , Michael Standing , Stanley Caine , Barry Cox , Harry Baird , George Innes , John Forgeham
summary: Charlie has a "job" to do. Having just left prison, he finds one of his friends has attempted a high-risk job in Italy right under the nose of the Mafia. Charlie's friend doesn't get very far, so Charlie takes over the "job". Using three Mini Coopers, a couple of Jaguars, and a bus, he hopes to bring Turin to a standstill, steal the gold, and escape.　　  查理有一份“工作”要做。刚离开监狱，他发现他的一个朋友在黑手党的眼皮底下试图在意大利从事一项高风险的工作。查理的朋友走得不远，所以查理接管了“工作”。他希望用三辆迷你库珀（Mini Coopers）、两辆美洲虎（Jaguar）和一辆公交车让都灵陷入瘫痪，抢走黄金，然后逃走。

title: The Italian Job (2003)
genre: 动作 犯罪 惊悚
cast: Donald Sutherland , Mark Wahlberg , Edward Norton , Charlize Theron , Jason Statham , Seth Green , Yasiin Bey , Fausto Callegarini , Stefano Petronelli , Fabio Scarpa , Cristiano Bonora , Tiberio Greco , Jimmy Shubert , Tammi Cubilette , Mary Portser , Shawn Fanning , Christopher Moore Jr. , Terrelle Jones
summary: Led by John Bridger (Donald Sutherland) and Charlie Croker (Mark Wahlberg) a team is assembled for one last heist to steal $35 million in gold bars from a heavily guarded safe in Venice, Italy. After successfully pulling off the heist, a team member, Steve (Edward Norton), driven by greed and jealousy, arranges to take the gold for himself and eliminate the remaining members of the group. Thinking the team dead, he returns to Los Angeles with the gold. Charlie and the survivors of this betrayal follow Steve to L.A. to exact revenge against the traitor. Charlie enlists the help of John Bridger's daughter, Stella (Charlize Theron) - a professional safe cracker - to get revenge. With Stella and the hacking skills of Lyle (Seth Green), the explosives skills of "Left Ear" (Yasiin Bey), and the driving skills of "Handsome" Rob (Jason Statham) this new team plans and executes a daring heist that weaves through the freeways and subways of L.A.　　  在约翰·布里杰（唐纳德·萨瑟兰饰）和查理·克罗克（马克·沃尔伯格饰）的带领下，一支队伍正在意大利威尼斯一家戒备森严的保险箱里进行最后一次抢劫，盗窃价值3500万美元的金条。在成功完成劫案后，团队成员史蒂夫（爱德华·诺顿饰）在贪婪和嫉妒的驱使下，安排将金牌据为己有，并除掉团队中的其余成员。认为球队已经死了，他带着金牌回到了洛杉矶。查理和这次背叛的幸存者跟随史蒂夫前往洛杉矶，对叛徒进行报复。查理寻求约翰·布里奇（John Bridger）的女儿斯特拉（Charlize Theron饰）的帮助，斯特拉是一名专业的安全破坏者，他想报复。凭借斯特拉和莱尔（赛斯·格林饰）的黑客技能、“左耳”（亚辛·贝伊饰）的爆炸技能以及“帅哥”罗布（杰森·斯塔瑟姆饰）的驾驶技能，这支新团队策划并实施了一场穿越洛杉矶高速公路和地铁的大胆抢劫。

summary: In Moscow, the FBI and their Russian counterpart, the MVD, are working on a joint mission to apprehend Russian mobster Ghazzi Murad specifically for the murder of Mayor Nikolai Semankho. During the arrest, they are forced to kill Ghazzi. Ghazzi's brother, Terek Murad, also a mobster, begins his own form of deadly retribution against the MVD for Ghazzi's death. But the FBI and MVD also get wind that Terek has hired an assassin by the code name Jackal to carry out a hit on a high profile but unknown American target for the Americans sticking their nose in Russian affairs. Intelligence points to that target being Donald Brown, the Director of the FBI. The Jackal is known only by name and reputation but no one in authority knows who he is, what he looks like or if he even really exists. They learn of only one person alive who they know has had ties to the Jackal

title: The Karate Kid (1984)
genre: 动作 剧情 家庭
cast: Ralph Macchio , Pat Morita , Elisabeth Shue , Martin Kove , Randee Heller , William Zabka , Ron Thomas , Rob Garrison , Chad McQueen , Tony O'Dell , Israel Juarbe , William Bassett , Larry B. Scott , Juli Fields , Dana Andersen , Frank Burt Avalon , Jeff Fishman , Ken Daly
summary: Daniel and his mother move from New Jersey to California. She has a wonderful new job, but Daniel quickly discovers that a dark haired Italian boy with a Jersey accent doesn't fit into the blond surfer crowd. Daniel manages to talk his way out of some fights, but he is finally cornered by several who belong to the same karate school. As Daniel is passing out from the beating he sees Miyagi, the elderly gardener leaps into the fray and save him by outfighting half a dozen teenagers. Miyagi and Daniel soon find out the real motivator behind the boys' violent attitude in the form of their karate teacher. Miyagi promises to teach Daniel karate and arranges a fight at the all-valley tournament some months off. When his training begins, Daniel doesn't understand what he is being shown. Miyagi seems more interested in having Daniel paint fences and wax cars than teaching him Karate.　　  丹尼尔和他的母亲从新泽西搬到加利福尼亚。她有一份很棒的新工作，但丹尼尔很快发现，一个带泽西口音的深色头发的意大利男孩不适合金发冲浪爱好者。丹尼尔设法摆脱了一些打斗，但最终被同一空手道学校的几个人逼到了绝境。当丹尼尔从被殴打中昏倒时，他看到了宫城县，这位年迈的园丁跳进了争斗中，并扑灭了六名青少年，救了他一命。宫城和丹尼尔很快就从空手道老师的身上发现了男孩们暴力态度背后的真正动机。宫城县承诺教丹尼尔空手道，并安排几个月后在全谷锦标赛上进行一场比赛。当丹尼尔开始训练时，他不明白自己在表演什么。比起教丹尼尔空手道，宫城似乎对丹尼尔油漆栅栏和打蜡汽车更感兴趣。

title: The Blind Side (2009)
genre: 传记 剧情 运动
cast: Quinton Aaron , Sandra Bullock , Tim McGraw , Jae Head , Lily Collins , Ray McKinnon , Kim Dickens , Adriane Lenox , Kathy Bates , Catherine Dyer , Andy Stahl , Tom Nowicki , Libby Whittemore , Brian Hollan , Melody Weintraub , Sharon Conley , Omar J. Dorsey , Paul Amadi
summary: Based on the true story of Leigh Anne Tuohy and Sean Tuohy who take in a homeless teenage African-American, Michael Oher. Michael has no idea who his father is and his mother is a drug addict. Michael has had little formal education and few skills to help him learn. Leigh Anne soon takes charge however, as is her nature, ensuring that the young man has every opportunity to succeed. When he expresses an interest in football, she goes all out to help him, including giving the coach a few ideas on how best to use Michael's skills. They not only provide him with a loving home, but hire a tutor to help him improve his grades to the point where he would qualify for an NCAA Division I athletic scholarship. Michael Oher was the first-round pick of the Baltimore Ravens in the 2009 NFL draft.　　  根据莉·安妮·托伊和肖恩·托伊的真实故事改编，他们收养了无家可归的非洲裔美国人迈克尔·奥赫。迈克尔不知道他的父亲是谁，而他的母亲是个瘾君子。迈克尔几乎没有受过正规教育，也没有什么技能可以帮助他学习。然而，利·安妮（Leigh Anne）很快就掌握了主动权，这是她的天性，确保了这位年轻人有一切成功的机会。当他表示对足球感兴趣时，她会全力以赴帮助他，包括给教练一些关于如何最好地运用迈克尔的技能的想法。他们不仅为他提供了一个充满爱的家，还聘请了一名导师帮助他提高成绩，使他有资格获得NCAA一级体育奖学金。迈克尔·奥赫（Michael Oher）是2009年NFL选秀中巴尔的摩乌鸦队（Baltimore Ravens）的第一轮选秀选手。

title: Chau tin dik tung wa (1987)
genre: 剧情 爱情
cast: Chow Yun-Fat , Cherie Chung , Danny Bak-Keung Chan , Gigi Suk Yee Wong , Fu-Sheng Wu , Yung-Cho Ching , Man Huang , Ming-Suen Jeng , Brenda Lo , George Gerard , Ozzy Kid
summary: Hong Kong native Jennifer (Cherie Chung) moves to New York City to study for her Master's Degree and to reunite with her boyfriend Vincent (Danny Chan Bak-Keung). There, she meets her very distant relative Samuel Pang (Yun-Fat Chow), a street smart and wise-talking waiter-by-day and gambler-by-night, who helps Jennifer settle in her apartment building in the outskirts of Brooklyn. When Jennifer discovers that Vincent is being unfaithful, she nearly puts all her plans to a halt. But, Pang talks sense into her and helps her adjust to her new life in the Big Apple and without Vincent, resulting in an unlikely relationship.　　  香港本地人詹妮弗（Cherie Chung）搬到纽约攻读硕士学位，并与男友文森特（Danny Chan Bak-Keung）团聚。在那里，她遇到了她的远房亲戚彭日成（周润发饰），他是一个聪明的街头侍者，也是一个夜以继日的赌徒，帮助詹妮弗在布鲁克林郊区的公寓里安顿下来。当詹妮弗发现文森特不忠时，她几乎停止了所有计划。但是，彭日成对她讲得很有道理，帮助她适应在纽约的新生活，而没有文森特，这导致了一段不太可能的关系。

title: Hearts Around the Table
genre: 爱情
cast: Ashley Newbrough , Steve Lund , Mindy Cohn , Mishael Morgan , Jake Epstein , Kathryn Davis , Al Mukadam , Justice James , Eve Crawford , Gillian Mauro , Kato Alexander , Klé McKoy , Marie Dame
summary: This first story about the foster children of Angie Hartman - their family which has continued to support each other and to convene for Sunday dinners even with the children now mostly being adults - centers on event planner Jenna Whitaker, who has her own consulting firm, Thistlebird Marketing. She is willing to work Sundays even at the expense of having dinner with family so that she can make a name for herself and Thistlebird. Her current client is tech billionaire Tom Redlands, she to organize a fundraising event for his new non-profit centered on underprivileged families. In what she thought was going to be her first face-to-face meeting with Tom, she instead meets with Tom's management consultant who is to be Jenna's liaison to the company. He just happens to be Andrew Clarington, Jenna's high school sweetheart, who she was in love with at the time, that is until he broke up with her immediately after graduation. As such, Andrew has largely been known by Jenna's family as the heartbreaker type who cannot be trusted, a view especially by foster sister Shari. Drew, however, had an altruistic motive for ending their relationship which he never mentioned to her, and was in turn in love with her, those feelings which reemerge upon their meeting again. Beyond if Jenna can get over the heartbreak she felt the first time, Jenna and Drew getting back together as a couple is threatened by another man subsequently entering Jenna's life who expresses an interest in her romantically, namely Tom.　　  这是关于安吉·哈特曼（Angie Hartman）的养子的第一个故事，他们的家人一直相互支持，并在周日聚餐，即使孩子现在大多是成年人。故事的中心是活动策划人詹娜·惠特克（Jenna Whitaker），她有自己的咨询公司Thistlebird Marketing。她愿意在周日工作，甚至不惜与家人共进晚餐，这样她就能为自己和蓟鸟出名。她的现任客户是科技界亿万富翁汤姆·雷德兰，她将为他的新非营利组织组织一次筹款活动，该组织以贫困家庭为中心。她本以为这将是她与汤姆的第一次面对面的会面，但她却会见了汤姆的管理顾问，他将成为珍娜与公司的联络人。他只是碰巧是杰娜的高中恋人安德鲁·克拉林顿，她当时爱上了他，直到他毕业后立即与她分手。正因为如此，安德鲁在詹娜的家人中被称为心碎型的人，不可信任，这一观点尤其被养育妹妹莎莉所认同。然而，德鲁有一个利他主义动机，想要结束他们之间的关系，但他从未向她提过，他反过来爱上了她，这种感情在他们再次见面时再次融合。除了詹娜能否克服她第一次感到的心碎之外，詹娜和德鲁重归于好的时候受到了另一个男人的威胁，这个男人随后进入了詹娜的生活，他对詹娜表现出了浪漫的兴趣，那就是汤姆。

summary: After losing her laundry store to a fire incident, a single mom Deok-hee receives a call from a bank offering a generous upfront loan so she takes it right away. But soon after, she finds out that she has become a victim of a voice phishing scheme. At the moment of despair, Jae-min, the phisher who tricked her, rings her phone once again to tip Deok-hee off about the criminal organization that locked him up and coerced him to make voice phishing calls from China. With that call, Deok-hee makes up her mind to investigate this case for herself and take a plane to China with her friends.　　  在一场火灾中失去了洗衣店后，一位单身母亲Deok-hee接到一家银行的电话，该银行提供了一笔慷慨的预付贷款，所以她立即接受了。但不久之后，她发现自己成了语音钓鱼计划的受害者。在绝望的时刻，欺骗她的钓鱼者Jae-min再次拨打电话，向Deok-hee举报将他关起来的犯罪组织，并强迫他从中国拨打语音钓鱼电话。接到电话后，Deok-hee决定亲自调查此案，并与她的朋友一起乘飞机前往中国。

summary: "I deliver everything that the post office service does not handle." Eun-ha, who is a normal junkyard employee, secretly works as a delivery clerk that deals with unusual delivery requests. One day, Eun-ha heads to Seoul to pick up a client who is involved in a gambling crime that wants to flee overseas. summary: Set in 2031, the entire world is frozen except for those aboard the Snowpiercer. For seventeen years, the world's survivors are on a train hurtling around the globe creating their own economy and class system. Led by Curtis (Chris Evans), a group of lower-class citizens living in squalor at the back of the train are determined to get to the front of the train and spread the wealth around. Each section of the train holds new surprises for the group who have to battle their way through. A revolution is underway.　　  设定在2031年，整个世界都被冰冻了，唯独雪崩号上的人除外。十七年来，世界上的幸存者一直坐在一列疾驰全球的火车上，创造自己的经济和阶级体系。在柯蒂斯（克里斯·埃文斯饰）的带领下，一群生活在火车尾部肮脏环境中的下层公民决心走到火车前部，把财富分散开来。火车的每一段都为那些必须奋战到底的人带来了新的惊喜。一场革命正在进行。

title: Desperately Seeking Susan (1985)
genre: 喜剧 剧情
cast: Rosanna Arquette , Madonna , Aidan Quinn , Mark Blum , Robert Joy , Laurie Metcalf , Anna Thomson , Will Patton , Peter Maloney , Steven Wright , John Turturro , Anne Carlisle , José Angel Santana , Giancarlo Esposito , Richard Hell , Rockets Redglare , Steve Bosh , Daisy Bradford
summary: Housewife Roberta Glass of Fort Lee, New Jersey, is feeling restless in her life, where she has not taken any chances, including in her marriage to home spa retailer Gary Glass, who knows what to expect in her every move, and who is more concerned about his public image with respect to his business than her. If being honest, Gary would consider her uptight. She does have a few diversions, one of her favorite being reading the personal classifieds, most specifically those written by someone named Jim whose ads are always titled "Desperately Seeking Susan". Roberta gleans that Jim and Susan are in a relationship of sorts with the ads the only way for him to get in touch with her as she travels around the country. Obsessed with the pair, Roberta decides to go to Battery Park when the latest ad requests Susan meet Jim there. In her sighting from afar, Roberta can see that Susan is a wild, new wavish attired woman, to some extent a polar opposite to Roberta herself. Out of circumstance, Roberta is able to purchase Susan's easily identifiable leather jacket from a third party, which in the process leads to Roberta getting amnesia, further resulting in her being able to obtain all of Susan's personal possessions, making her believe that she must be who these possessions point to her being. This causes some confusion for Dez, a friend of Jim's who has never met Susan, and who Jim, a rock musician, asked to look after Susan in his needed absence out of town for a gig. Dez, a movie projectionist, can't help but fall for Roberta who he believes is Susan, while Roberta, in her newfound freedom, falls for Dez in return. What Roberta is unaware of, even before her amnesia, is that a criminal, Wayne Nolan, who has already killed once, is after Susan with regard to some priceless Egyptian earrings Susan has out of circumstance, he only knowing her from that iconic leather jacket. Susan does eventually learn this information about Wayne and thus tries to track down this mysterious woman who has stolen her possessions both to get back her stuff but also warn her about Wayne. Matters will only get more complicated as Gary gets closer to tracking down his missing wife, when Jim comes back into town looking for Susan, and if and when Roberta regains her memory.　　  新泽西州李堡市的家庭主妇罗伯塔·格拉斯（Roberta Glass）在她的生活中感到焦躁不安，她没有抓住任何机会，包括与家庭水疗零售商加里·格拉斯的婚姻，她知道自己的一举一动都会带来什么样的结果，她比她更关心他在事业方面的公众形象。如果说实话，加里会认为她很紧张。她确实有一些消遣，其中一个她最喜欢的是阅读个人分类广告，尤其是那些由一个叫吉姆的人写的广告，其标题总是“拼命寻找苏珊”。罗伯塔了解到吉姆和苏珊与广告有着某种关系，这是他在她周游全国时与她联系的唯一途径。罗伯塔被这对情侣迷住了，当最新的广告要求苏珊在巴特利公园与吉姆见面时，她决定去那里。从罗伯塔远处的视线中，她可以看到苏珊是一个狂野的、新来的波浪装女人，在某种程度上与罗伯塔本人截然不同。在这种情况下，罗伯塔能够从第三方购买苏珊易于识别的皮夹克，这导致罗伯塔患上健忘症，进而导致她能够获得苏珊的所有个人财产，使她相信自己一定是这些财产所指向的人。这给杰姆的朋友德兹（Dez）带来了一些困惑，他从未见过苏珊，而摇滚音乐家杰姆（Jim）则要求德兹在必要的外出演出时照顾苏珊。德兹是一名电影放映员，他情不自禁地爱上了罗伯塔，他认为罗伯塔就是苏珊，而罗伯塔在新获得的自由中也爱上了德兹。罗伯塔甚至在失忆症之前都不知道的是，一名已经杀害过一次的罪犯韦恩·诺兰（Wayne Nolan）正在追捕苏珊，因为苏珊有一些无价的埃及耳环，他只是从那件标志性的皮夹克中认识她。苏珊最终确实了解到了有关韦恩的信息，因此她试图追查到这个神秘的女人，她偷走了自己的财产，不仅是为了取回她的东西，还警告她注意韦恩。当加里离追寻失踪妻子越来越近，当吉姆回到镇上寻找苏珊，当罗伯塔恢复记忆时，事情只会变得更加复杂。

title: The Blind Side (2009)
genre: 传记 剧情 运动
cast: Quinton Aaron , Sandra Bullock , Tim McGraw , Jae Head , Lily Collins , Ray McKinnon , Kim Dickens , Adriane Lenox , Kathy Bates , Catherine Dyer , Andy Stahl , Tom Nowicki , Libby Whittemore , Brian Hollan , Melody Weintraub , Sharon Conley , Omar J. Dorsey , Paul Amadi
summary: Based on the true story of Leigh Anne Tuohy and Sean Tuohy who take in a homeless teenage African-American, Michael Oher. Michael has no idea who his father is and his mother is a drug addict. Michael has had little formal education and few skills to help him learn. Leigh Anne soon takes charge however, as is her nature, ensuring that the young man has every opportunity to succeed. When he expresses an interest in football, she goes all out to help him, including giving the coach a few ideas on how best to use Michael's skills. They not only provide him with a loving home, but hire a tutor to help him improve his grades to the point where he would qualify for an NCAA Division I athletic scholarship. Michael Oher was the first-round pick of the Baltimore Ravens in the 2009 NFL draft.　　  根据莉·安妮·托伊和肖恩·托伊的真实故事改编，他们收养了无家可归的非洲裔美国人迈克尔·奥赫。迈克尔不知道他的父亲是谁，而他的母亲是个瘾君子。迈克尔几乎没有受过正规教育，也没有什么技能可以帮助他学习。然而，利·安妮（Leigh Anne）很快就掌握了主动权，这是她的天性，确保了这位年轻人有一切成功的机会。当他表示对足球感兴趣时，她会全力以赴帮助他，包括给教练一些关于如何最好地运用迈克尔的技能的想法。他们不仅为他提供了一个充满爱的家，还聘请了一名导师帮助他提高成绩，使他有资格获得NCAA一级体育奖学金。迈克尔·奥赫（Michael Oher）是2009年NFL选秀中巴尔的摩乌鸦队（Baltimore Ravens）的第一轮选秀选手。

genre: 剧情
cast: Makayla McIntosh , Anthony Dain , Jacque Laon Horton II , Danielle Braund , Cat Yudain , Emily Blake Anderson , Emily Chamberlin , Amy Fess , Tristan Rose Gillia , Bailey Kathryn , Susanne McDonald , Ibrahim Noccioli , Grace Stroke , Emelia Sherin , Carlie Allen , Nick Z Allen , Carter Coleman , Rick Davis
summary: After a near-fatal accident, Riley finds herself escaping to Rockaway Beach, NY. She is searching for a new-normal in the waves of the ocean by taking up surfing as a hobby. At the same time, Logan is searching for the same solace Riley seeks in the waves while he is recovering from rare male breast cancer surgery and awaiting news on whether or not he is cancer free. What starts as two souls running from their respective lives becomes a journey of hope, friendship, healing and the realization that we are stronger than the things that hurt us.　　  在一场几乎致命的事故后，莱利发现自己逃到了纽约州的罗克韦海滩。她把冲浪作为一种爱好，在大海的波涛中寻找新常态。与此同时，洛根正在寻找莱利从罕见的男性乳腺癌手术中恢复过来时所寻求的安慰，并等待关于他是否没有癌症的消息。从两个灵魂逃离各自的生命开始，这是一段充满希望、友谊、治愈和意识到我们比伤害我们的东西更强大的旅程。
